#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:136
msgid ":ref:`Order confirmation <ecommerce/checkout/order_confirmation>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Confirmation de commande <ecommerce/checkout/order_confirmation>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:140
msgid ""
"Each step can be customized using the website editor by "
"adding :doc:`building blocks <../website/web_design/building_blocks>` or "
"opening the :guilabel:`Customize` tab to enable various checkout options."
msgstr ""
"Chaque étape peut être personnalisée à l'aide de l'éditeur de site Web en "
"ajoutant des :doc:`blocs de construction <../website/web_design/"
"building_blocks>` ou en ouvrant l'onglet :guilabel:`Personnaliser` pour "
"activer diverses options de commande."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:145
msgid "Content added through building blocks is **specific** to each step."
msgstr ""
"Le contenu ajouté via des blocs de construction est **spécifique** à chaque "
"étape."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:148
msgid ""
"Restrict access to the :ref:`shop <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>` "
"and :ref:`checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>` for "
"specific customers, e.g., in a :doc:`B2B <b2b_b2c>` business setup."
msgstr ""
"Restreindre l'accès à la :ref:`boutique <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-"
"access>` et au :ref:`paiement <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>` "
"pour des clients spécifiques, par exemple dans une configuration d'activité "
":doc:`B2B <b2b_b2c>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:155
msgid "Review order"
msgstr "Vérifier la commande"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:157
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Review Order` step allows customers to see the items they "
"added to their cart, adjust quantities, or :guilabel:`Remove` products. "
"Information related to the product prices and taxes applied are also "
"displayed. Customers can then click the :guilabel:`Checkout` button to "
"continue to the :ref:`Delivery <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>` step."
msgstr ""
"L'étape :guilabel:`Vérifier la commande` permet aux clients de voir les "
"articles qu'ils ont ajoutés à leur panier, d'ajuster les quantités ou de "
":guilabel:`Retirer` des produits. Les informations relatives aux prix des "
"produits et aux taxes appliquées sont également affichées. Les clients "
"peuvent ensuite cliquer sur le bouton :guilabel:`Commander` pour continuer "
"vers l'étape :ref:`Livraison <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:162
msgid ""
"Open the website editor to :ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` checkout options such as:"
msgstr ""
"Ouvrir l'éditeur de site web pour :ref:`activer <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` les options de paiement telles que :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:165
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Suggested Accessories`: to showcase :ref:`accessory products "
"<ecommerce/cross_upselling/accessory>`;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Accessoires suggérés` : pour mettre en avant les :ref:`produits "
"accessoires <ecommerce/cross_upselling/accessory>` ;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:167
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Promo Code`: to allow customers to redeem :ref:`gift cards "
"<ewallet_gift/gift-cards>` or apply :doc:`discount codes <../../sales/sales/"
"products_prices/loyalty_discount>`;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Code promo` : pour permettre aux clients d'utiliser des "
":ref:`cartes cadeaux <ewallet_gift/gift-cards>` ou d'appliquer des "
":doc:`codes de réduction <../../sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount>"
"` ;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:169
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add to Wishlist`: :ref:`Enable wishlists <ecommerce/products/"
"wishlists>` to allow signed-in users to remove a product from their cart and "
"add it to their wishlist using the :guilabel:`Save for later` option."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ajouter à la liste de souhaits` : :ref:`activez les listes de "
"souhaits <ecommerce/products/wishlists>` pour permettre aux utilisateurs "
"connectés de retirer un produit de leur panier et de l'ajouter à leur liste "
"de souhaits à l'aide de l'option :guilabel:`Enregistrer pour plus tard`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:174
msgid ""
"If a :doc:`fiscal position <../../finance/accounting/taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>` is detected automatically, the product tax is determined "
"based on the customer's IP address."
msgstr ""
"Si une :doc:`position fiscale <../../finance/accounting/taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>` est détectée automatiquement, la taxe du produit est "
"déterminée en fonction de l'adresse IP du client."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:176
msgid ""
"If the installed :doc:`payment provider <../../finance/payment_providers>` "
"supports :ref:`express checkout <payment_providers/express_checkout>`, a "
"dedicated button is displayed, allowing customers to go straight from the "
"cart to the confirmation page without filling out the contact form."
msgstr ""
"Si le :doc:`fournisseur de paiement <../../finance/payment_providers>` "
"installé prend en charge le :ref:`paiement express <payment_providers/"
"express_checkout>`, un bouton dédié s'affiche, permettant aux clients de "
"passer directement du panier à la page de confirmation sans remplir le "
"formulaire de contact."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:184
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:3
msgid "Delivery"
msgstr "Livraison"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:186
msgid "Once they have reviewed their order:"
msgstr "Une fois qu'ils ont examiné leur commande :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:188
msgid ""
"Unsigned-in customers are prompted to :guilabel:`Sign in` or enter "
"their :guilabel:`Email address`, along with their delivery address and phone "
"details;"
msgstr ""
"Les clients non connectés sont invités à :guilabel:`Se connecter` ou à "
"saisir leur :guilabel:`Adresse e-mail`, ainsi que leur adresse de livraison "
"et leurs coordonnées téléphoniques ;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:190
msgid ""
"Signed-in customers can select the appropriate :guilabel:`Delivery address`."
msgstr ""
"Les clients connectés peuvent sélectionner l':guilabel:`Adresse de "
"livraison` appropriée."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:192
msgid ""
"They can then :doc:`choose a delivery method <shipping>`, select or enter "
"their :guilabel:`Billing Address` (or toggle the :guilabel:`Same as delivery "
"address` switch if the billing and delivery addresses are identical), and "
"click :guilabel:`Confirm` to proceed to the next step."
msgstr ""
"Ils peuvent ensuite :doc:`choisir un mode de livraison <shipping>`, "
"sélectionner ou saisir leur :guilabel:`adresse de facturation` (ou activer "
"le bouton :guilabel:`identique à l'adresse de livraison` si les adresses de "
"facturation et de livraison sont identiques), puis cliquer sur "
":guilabel:`confirmer` pour passer à l'étape suivante."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:197
msgid ""
"For B2B customers, you can also :ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` optional :ref:`B2B fields <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/b2b-fields>` "
"in the website editor."
msgstr ""
"Pour les clients B2B, vous pouvez également :ref:`activer <ecommerce/"
"checkout/customize_steps>` des :ref:`champs B2B <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/b2b-"
"fields>` optionnels dans l'éditeur de site web."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:199
msgid ""
"You can add a checkbox for users without an account to sign up for a "
"newsletter. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`. Under the :guilabel:`Shop - Checkout Process` section, enable "
"the :guilabel:`Newsletter` feature and select a :guilabel:`Newsletter List`."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez ajouter une case à cocher pour que les utilisateurs sans compte "
"puissent s'inscrire à une newsletter. Pour ce faire, allez dans "
":menuselection:`Site Web --> Configuration --> Paramètres`. Dans la section "
":guilabel:`Boutique - Processus de commande`, activez la fonctionnalité "
":guilabel:`Newsletter` et sélectionnez une :guilabel:`Liste de newsletter`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:207
msgid "Extra info"
msgstr "Infos supplémentaires"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:209
msgid ""
"You can add an :guilabel:`Extra Info` step in the checkout process to "
"collect additional customer information through an online form, which is "
"then included in the :ref:`sales order <handling/sales>`. To do "
"so, :ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/customize_steps>` the :guilabel:`Extra "
"Step` option in the website editor. The form can be :ref:`customized "
"<website/building_blocks/form>` as needed."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez ajouter une étape :guilabel:`Infos supplémentaires` dans le "
"processus de commande pour collecter des informations client supplémentaires "
"via un formulaire en ligne, qui est ensuite inclus dans la :ref:`commande "
"client <handling/sales>`. Pour ce faire, :ref:`activez <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` l'option :guilabel:`Étape supplémentaire` dans l'éditeur "
"de site Web. Le formulaire peut être :ref:`personnalisé <website/"
"building_blocks/form>` selon les besoins."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:216
msgid ""
"Alternatively, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, scroll to the :guilabel:`Shop - Checkout Process` section, "
"enable :guilabel:`Extra Step During Checkout`, and click :guilabel:`Save`. "
"Click :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Configure Form` to customize it."
msgstr ""
"Alternativement, allez dans :menuselection:`Site Web --> Configuration --> "
"Paramètres`, faites défiler jusqu'à la section :guilabel:`Boutique - "
"Processus de commande`, activez :guilabel:`Étape supplémentaire lors de la "
"commande`, et cliquez sur :guilabel:`Enregistrer`. Cliquez sur :icon:`fa-"
"arrow-right` :guilabel:`Configurer le formulaire` pour le personnaliser."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:223
msgid "Payment"
msgstr "Paiement"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:225
msgid ""
"At the :guilabel:`Payment` step, customers :guilabel:`Choose a payment "
"method`, enter their payment details, and click :guilabel:`Pay now`."
msgstr ""
"À l'étape :guilabel:`Paiement`, les clients :guilabel:`Choisissent un mode "
"de paiement`, saisissent leurs informations de paiement et cliquent sur "
":guilabel:`Payer maintenant`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:228
msgid ""
"You can require customers to agree to your :doc:`terms and conditions <../../"
"finance/accounting/customer_invoices/terms_conditions>` before payment. "
"To :ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/customize_steps>` this option, go to the "
"website editor and toggle the :guilabel:`Accept Terms & Conditions` feature."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez exiger que les clients acceptent vos :doc:`conditions générales "
"<../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices/terms_conditions>` avant le "
"paiement. Pour :ref:`activer <ecommerce/checkout/customize_steps>` cette "
"option, allez dans l'éditeur de site Web et activez la fonctionnalité "
":guilabel:`Accepter les conditions générales`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:234
msgid ""
"Enable the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` and click the :icon:`fa-"
"bug` (:guilabel:`bug`) icon to display an :ref:`availability "
"<payment_providers/availability>` report for payment providers and payment "
"methods, which helps diagnose potential availability issues on the payment "
"form."
msgstr ""
"Activez le :ref:`mode développeur <developer-mode>` et cliquez sur l'icône "
":icon:`fa-bug` (:guilabel:`bug`) pour afficher un rapport de "
":ref:`disponibilité <payment_providers/availability>` des fournisseurs de "
"paiement et des modes de paiement, ce qui aide à diagnostiquer les problèmes "
"potentiels de disponibilité sur le formulaire de paiement."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:242
msgid "Order confirmation"
msgstr "Confirmation de commande"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:244
msgid ""
"The final step of the checkout process is the :guilabel:`Order "
"confirmation`, which provides a summary of the customer's purchase details."
msgstr ""
"La dernière étape du processus de commande est la :guilabel:`Confirmation de "
"commande`, qui fournit un résumé des détails d'achat du client."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:248
msgid ":doc:`Order handling documentation <order_handling>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Documentation sur le traitement des commandes <order_handling>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:3
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:124
msgid "Customer accounts"
msgstr "Comptes clients"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:5
msgid ""
"Using customer accounts for an ecommerce shop enables you to :ref:`manage "
"customers <ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-creation>`, control access to "
"the :ref:`shop <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>`, "
"the :ref:`checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>`, or "
"the :ref:`customer portal <portal/access>`, and support both :doc:`B2B and "
"B2C operations <b2b_b2c>`."
msgstr ""
"L'utilisation de comptes clients pour une boutique eCommerce vous permet de "
":ref:`gérer les clients <ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-creation>`, "
"contrôler l'accès à la :ref:`boutique <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-"
"access>`, au :ref:`paiement <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>`, "
"ou au :ref:`portail client <portal/access>`, et prendre en charge les "
":doc:`opérations B2B et B2C <b2b_b2c>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:11
msgid ""
"After logging in, customers can access their :doc:`customer portal <../../"
"general/users/portal>` by clicking their username in the top-right corner of "
"the screen and selecting :guilabel:`My Account`. From there, they can view "
"all their documents in one place, such as quotations, orders, invoices, and "
"more."
msgstr ""
"Après connexion, les clients peuvent accéder à leur :doc:`portail client <../"
"../general/users/portal>` en cliquant sur leur nom d'utilisateur dans le "
"coin supérieur droit de l'écran et en sélectionnant :guilabel:`Mon compte`. "
"De là, ils peuvent consulter tous leurs documents en un seul endroit, tels "
"que devis, commandes, factures, etc."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:None
msgid "Customer account access"
msgstr "Accès au compte client"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:20
msgid ""
"The customer account page can be customized with building blocks and other "
"features through the :doc:`website builder <../website/web_design>`."
msgstr ""
"La page du compte client peut être personnalisée avec des blocs de "
"construction et d'autres fonctionnalités via le :doc:`constructeur de site "
"Web <../website/web_design>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:26
msgid "Customer account creation"
msgstr "Création de compte client"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:28
msgid ""
"You can choose whether customer accounts and document access are available "
"to everyone or restricted to invited users only. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, then scroll down "
"to the :guilabel:`Privacy` section. Under :guilabel:`Customer Account`, "
"select one of the following options:"
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez choisir si les comptes clients et l'accès aux documents sont "
"disponibles pour tous ou réservés uniquement aux utilisateurs invités. Pour "
"ce faire, allez dans :menuselection:`Site Web --> Configuration --> "
"Paramètres`, puis faites défiler jusqu'à la section "
":guilabel:`Confidentialité`. Sous :guilabel:`Compte client`, sélectionnez "
"l'une des options suivantes :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:33
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On invitation`: Customers can only create an account if the "
"website owner sends them an invitation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sur invitation` : Les clients ne peuvent créer un compte que si "
"le propriétaire du site web leur envoie une invitation."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:35
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Free sign up`: Every website visitor can create an account and "
"sign in. They will get access to the :doc:`portal <../../general/users/"
"portal>` by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Inscription libre` : chaque visiteur du site Web peut créer un "
"compte et se connecter. Ils auront accès au :doc:`portail <../../general/"
"users/portal>` par défaut."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:40
msgid "To send an email invitation to a customer:"
msgstr "Pour envoyer une invitation par e-mail à un client :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:42
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Customers`."
msgstr "Allez dans :menuselection:`Site Web --> eCommerce --> Clients`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:43
msgid ""
"Select a customer or click :guilabel:`New` to create one, ensuring "
"an :guilabel:`Email` address is set."
msgstr ""
"Sélectionnez un client ou cliquez sur :guilabel:`Nouveau` pour en créer un, "
"en vous assurant qu'une adresse :guilabel:`E-mail` est définie."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:45
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(Actions)` icon next to the record's "
"name at the top-left and select :guilabel:`Grant portal access`."
msgstr ""
"Cliquez sur l'icône :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions` à côté du nom de "
"l'enregistrement en haut à gauche et sélectionnez :guilabel:`Accorder "
"l'accès portail`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:47
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Portal Access Management` pop-up, click :guilabel:`Grant "
"Access` to send the invitation."
msgstr ""
"Dans la fenêtre contextuelle :guilabel:`Gestion des accès portail`, cliquez "
"sur :guilabel:`Accorder l'accès` pour envoyer l'invitation."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:51
msgid ""
"To invite multiple customers at once, switch to the customers :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`List` view, select several customers, click the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Actions` button, and select :guilabel:`Grant portal access`."
msgstr ""
"Pour inviter plusieurs clients à la fois, passez à la vue :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`Liste` des clients, sélectionnez plusieurs clients, cliquez "
"sur le bouton :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions`, et sélectionnez "
":guilabel:`Accorder l'accès portail`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:55
msgid ""
"Once done, the customer(s) receive an email confirming their account "
"creation, including instructions on setting a password and activating their "
"account."
msgstr ""
"Une fois terminé, le ou les clients reçoivent un e-mail confirmant la "
"création de leur compte, incluant des instructions pour définir un mot de "
"passe et activer leur compte."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:59
msgid ""
"When selecting the :guilabel:`Free sign up`, a clickable :guilabel:`Don't "
"have an account?` link appears under the login form on the website."
msgstr ""
"Lors de la sélection de :guilabel:`Inscription libre`, un lien cliquable "
":guilabel:`Vous n'avez pas de compte ?` apparaît sous le formulaire de "
"connexion sur le site web."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:61
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`On invitation` option is especially useful for :ref:`B2B "
"<ecommerce/b2b_b2c/prices>` businesses that prefer to keep :ref:`prices "
"hidden <ecommerce/prices/hide-prices>` on the website and grant access only "
"to invited customers."
msgstr ""
"L'option :guilabel:`Sur invitation` est particulièrement utile pour les "
"entreprises :ref:`B2B <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/prices>` qui préfèrent "
":ref:`masquer les prix <ecommerce/prices/hide-prices>` sur le site web et "
"accorder l'accès uniquement aux clients invités."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:66
msgid ""
"It is possible to configure a website form with a :guilabel:`Create a "
"Customer` :ref:`action <website/building_blocks/action>` to automatically "
"create a customer record in the backend when filled in."
msgstr ""
"Il est possible de configurer un formulaire de site web avec une "
":ref:`action <website/building_blocks/action>` :guilabel:`Créer un client` "
"pour créer automatiquement un enregistrement client dans le backend "
"lorsqu'il est rempli."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:71
msgid "Access restriction"
msgstr "Restriction d'accès"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:73
msgid ""
"Once a customer account is created, it is still possible to adjust the "
"access rights either globally or for individual users:"
msgstr ""
"Une fois un compte client créé, il est toujours possible d'ajuster les "
"droits d'accès soit globalement soit pour des utilisateurs individuels :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:76
msgid ""
":ref:`Revoke access or re-invite a customer <portal/access>` using the "
"related buttons in the :guilabel:`Portal Access Management` pop-up."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Révoquer l'accès ou réinviter un client <portal/access>` à l'aide des "
"boutons correspondants dans la fenêtre :guilabel:`Gestion des accès au "
"portail`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:78
msgid ""
"Restrict :ref:`access to the shop <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>`;"
msgstr ""
"Restreindre :ref:`l'accès à la boutique <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-"
"access>` ;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:79
msgid ""
"Decide whether customers need to create an account to :ref:`complete the "
"checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>`."
msgstr ""
"Décider si les clients doivent créer un compte pour :ref:`finaliser le "
"paiement <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:83
msgid ""
"It is also possible to define the types of documents customers have access "
"to. To do so, click your username in the upper-right corner of the website, "
"select :guilabel:`My Account` and open the :doc:`website builder <../website/"
"web_design>`. On the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, enable or disable access to "
"specific documents as needed."
msgstr ""
"Il est également possible de définir les types de documents auxquels les "
"clients ont accès. Pour ce faire, cliquez sur votre nom d'utilisateur dans "
"le coin supérieur droit du site Web, sélectionnez :guilabel:`Mon compte` et "
"ouvrez le :doc:`constructeur de site Web <../website/web_design>`. Dans "
"l'onglet :guilabel:`Personnaliser`, activez ou désactivez l'accès à des "
"documents spécifiques selon vos besoins."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:91
msgid "Shop access"
msgstr "Accès à la boutique"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:93
msgid ""
"To restrict access to the entire online shop for users who are not logged-"
"in, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll "
"to :guilabel:`Privacy` and under :guilabel:`Ecommerce Access`, "
"select :guilabel:`Logged in users`. Select :guilabel:`All users` if the shop "
"should be visible to every website visitor."
msgstr ""
"Pour restreindre l'accès à l'ensemble de la boutique en ligne aux "
"utilisateurs qui ne sont pas connectés, allez dans :menuselection:`Site "
"Web --> Configuration --> Paramètres`, faites défiler jusqu'à "
":guilabel:`Confidentialité` et sous :guilabel:`Accès eCommerce`, "
"sélectionnez :guilabel:`Utilisateurs connectés`. Sélectionnez "
":guilabel:`Tous les utilisateurs` si la boutique doit être visible par tous "
"les visiteurs du site Web."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:99
msgid ""
"To restrict access to the shop's pricing, use :ref:`pricelists <ecommerce/"
"prices/pricelists>` with :ref:`country groups <ecommerce/prices/country-"
"groups>`."
msgstr ""
"Pour restreindre l'accès aux prix de la boutique, utiliser les :ref:`listes "
"de prix <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` avec les :ref:`groupes de pays "
"<ecommerce/prices/country-groups>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:105
msgid "Checkout access"
msgstr "Accès au paiement"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:107
msgid ""
"To allow customers to checkout as guests or force them to sign in/create an "
"account, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, "
"scroll down to the :guilabel:`Shop - Checkout Process` section, and "
"configure the :guilabel:`Sign in/up at checkout` setting. The following "
"options are available:"
msgstr ""
"Pour permettre aux clients de passer commande en tant qu'invités ou les "
"obliger à se connecter/créer un compte, allez dans :menuselection:`Site "
"Web --> Configuration --> Paramètres`, faites défiler jusqu'à la section "
":guilabel:`Boutique - Processus de commande`, et configurez le paramètre "
":guilabel:`Se connecter/s'inscrire lors du paiement`. Les options suivantes "
"sont disponibles :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:112
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Optional`: Customers can check out as guests and register later "
"via the order confirmation email to track their order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Facultatif` : Les clients peuvent payer en tant qu'invités et "
"s'inscrire plus tard via l'e-mail de confirmation de commande pour suivre "
"leur commande."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:114
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Disabled (buy as guest)`: Customers can checkout as guests "
"without creating an account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Désactivé (achat en tant qu'invité)` : Les clients peuvent passer "
"commande en tant qu'invités sans créer de compte."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:115
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Mandatory (no guest checkout)`: Customers must sign in or create "
"an account at the :ref:`Review Order <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>` step "
"to complete their purchase."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Obligatoire (pas de commande invité)` : Les clients doivent se "
"connecter ou créer un compte à l'étape :ref:`Vérifier la commande <ecommerce/"
"checkout/review_order>` pour finaliser leur achat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:119
msgid ""
"Settings are specific to each website, allowing you to configure a B2C "
"website with guest checkout and a B2B website that requires customers to "
"sign in."
msgstr ""
"Les paramètres sont spécifiques à chaque site, permettant de configurer un "
"site B2C avec paiement invité et un site B2B nécessitant que les clients se "
"connectent."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:121
msgid ""
"To use the :ref:`wishlist <ecommerce/products/wishlists>` feature, customers "
"must create an account to save their favorite items for later."
msgstr ""
"Pour utiliser la fonctionnalité de :ref:`liste de souhaits <ecommerce/"
"products/wishlists>`, les clients doivent créer un compte pour enregistrer "
"leurs articles favoris pour plus tard."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:127
msgid "Multi-website account"
msgstr "Compte multi-sites"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:129
msgid ""
"When managing multiple websites, it is possible to make customer accounts "
"available across *all* websites, allowing each customer to use a single "
"account. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, in the :guilabel:`Privacy` section, enable the :guilabel:`Shared "
"Customer Accounts` option."
msgstr ""
"Lors de la gestion de plusieurs sites Web, il est possible de rendre les "
"comptes clients disponibles sur *tous* les sites Web, permettant à chaque "
"client d'utiliser un seul compte. Pour ce faire, allez dans "
":menuselection:`Site Web --> Configuration --> Paramètres`, dans la section "
":guilabel:`Confidentialité`, activez l'option :guilabel:`Comptes clients "
"partagés`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:135
msgid ""
"When operating both :ref:`B2B and B2C online shops <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/"
"multiple-websites>`, it is recommended to use separate websites for each "
"business model."
msgstr ""
"Lors de l'exploitation de :ref:`boutiques en ligne B2B et B2C <ecommerce/"
"b2b_b2c/multiple-websites>`, il est recommandé d'utiliser des sites "
"distincts pour chaque modèle économique."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:3
msgid "Order handling"
msgstr "Gérer des commandes"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:5
msgid ""
"When a customer orders on your eCommerce, there are **three** record types "
"required to be handle in Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"Lorsqu'un client passe une commande auprès de votre eCommerce, **trois** "
"types d'enregistrements nécessaires doivent être gérés dans Odoo :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:8
msgid ":ref:`Sales orders <handling/sales>`;"
msgstr ":ref:`Bons de commande <handling/sales>` ;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:9
msgid ":ref:`Delivery orders <handling/delivery>`;"
msgstr ":ref:`Bons de livraison <handling/delivery>` ;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:10
msgid ":ref:`Invoices & legal requirements <handling/legal>`."
msgstr ":ref:`Factures & exigences légales <handling/legal>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:15
msgid "Sales orders"
msgstr "Commandes clients"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:18
msgid "Order and payment status"
msgstr "Statut de la commande et du paiement"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:20
msgid ""
"The first step when a customer adds a product to his cart is the creation of "
"a quotation. Orders can be managed either from the **Website** "
"or :doc:`Sales </applications/sales/sales>` app. eCommerce orders can "
"automatically be assigned to a specific sales team by going "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`. In the **Shop - "
"Checkout Process** section, select a :guilabel:`Sales Team` "
"or :guilabel:`Salesperson` to handle eCommerce orders."
msgstr ""
"La première chose à faire lorsqu'un client ajoute un produit à son panier "
"est de créer un devis. Il est possible de gérer les commandes à partir de "
"l'application **Site Web** ou :doc:`Ventes </applications/sales/sales>`. Les "
"commandes eCommerce peuvent être assignées automatiquement à une équipe "
"commerciale spécifique en allant à :menuselection:`Site Web --> "
"Configuration --> Paramètres`. Dans la section **Boutique - Processus de "
"paiement**, sélectionnez une :guilabel:`Équipe commerciale` ou "
"un :guilabel:`Vendeur` pour gérer les commandes eCommerce."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:None
msgid "Assignment of online orders to a sales team or salesperson"
msgstr ""
"Assignation des commandes en ligne à une équipe commerciale ou un vendeur"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:30
msgid ""
"Orders can be found under :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Orders/"
"Unpaid Orders`. Each order goes through a different status:"
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez trouver les commandes dans :menuselection:`Site Web --> "
"eCommerce --> Commandes/Commandes non payées`. Chaque commande passe par un "
"statut différent :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:33
msgid ""
"**Quotation**: a new product is added to the cart, but the customer has "
"*not* gone through the checkout process yet;"
msgstr ""
"**Devis** : un nouveau produit est ajouté au panier, mais le client n'a "
"*pas* encore procédé au paiement ;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:35
msgid ""
"**Quotation sent**: the customer has gone through the checkout process and "
"confirmed the order, but the payment is not yet confirmed;"
msgstr ""
"**Devis envoyé** : le client a procédé au paiement et a confirmé la "
"commande, mais le paiement n'est pas encore confirmé ;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:37
msgid ""
"**Order**: the customer has gone through the checkout process, confirmed the "
"order, and the payment is received."
msgstr ""
"**Commande** : le client a procédé au paiement, confirmé la commande et le "
"paiement est reçu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:None
msgid "Statuses of eCommerce orders"
msgstr "Statuts des commandes eCommerce"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:45
msgid "Abandoned cart"
msgstr "Paniers abandonnés"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:47
msgid ""
"An **abandoned cart** represents an order for which the customer did **not "
"finish** the checkout confirmation process. For these orders, it is possible "
"to send an **email reminder** to the customer automatically. To enable that "
"feature, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings` and "
"in the :guilabel:`Email & Marketing` section, "
"enable :guilabel:`Automatically send abandoned checkout emails`. Once "
"enabled, you can set the **time-lapse** after which the email is sent and "
"customize the **email template** used."
msgstr ""
"Un **panier abandonné** représente une commande pour laquelle le client "
"**n'a pas terminé** le processus de paiement. Pour ces commandes, il est "
"possible d'envoyer automatiquement un **rappel par e-mail** au client. Pour "
"activer cette fonctionnalité, allez à :menuselection:`Site Web --> "
"Configuration --> Paramètres` et dans la section :guilabel:`E-mail & "
"Marketing`, activez :guilabel:`Envoyer automatiquement des e-mails en cas de "
"paiement abandonné`. Une fois cette option activée, vous pouvez définir le "
"**laps de temps** après lequel l'e-mail est envoyé et vous pouvez "
"personnaliser le **modèle d'e-mail** utilisé."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:55
msgid ""
"For abandoned cart emails, the customer must either have entered their "
"contact details during the checkout process; or be logged-in when they added "
"the product to their cart."
msgstr ""
"En ce qui concerne les e-mails envoyés en cas de panier abandonné, le client "
"doit avoir donné ses coordonnées pendant le processus de paiement ou il doit "
"être connecté quand il a ajouté le produit à son panier."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:61
msgid "Delivery orders"
msgstr "Bons de livraison"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:64
msgid "Delivery flow"
msgstr "Flux de livraison"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:66
msgid ""
"Once a quotation has been confirmed, a delivery order is automatically "
"created. The next step is to process this delivery."
msgstr ""
"Une fois qu'un devis a été confirmé, un bon de livraison est créé "
"automatiquement. La prochaine étape consiste à procéder à la livraison."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:69
msgid ""
"Packing eCommerce orders usually requires picking the product, preparing the "
"packaging, printing the shipping label(s) and shipping to the customer. "
"Depending on the number of orders, strategy, or resources, those steps can "
"be considered as one or multiple actions in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"L'emballage des commandes eCommerce demande également le transfert du "
"produit, la préparation du colisage, l'impression de la ou des étiquettes "
"d'expédition et l'expédition au client. En fonction du nombre de commandes, "
"de la stratégie ou des ressources, ces étapes peuvent être considérées comme "
"une ou plusieurs actions dans Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:73
msgid ""
"An automatic email can be sent to the customer when the transfer status in "
"Odoo is “done”. To do so, enable the feature in the settings of "
"the :doc:`Inventory </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory>` app."
msgstr ""
"Un e-mail automatique peut être envoyé au client lorsque le statut du "
"transfert dans Odoo est \"fait\". Pour ce faire, activez la fonctionnalité "
"dans les paramètres de l'application :doc:`Inventaire </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:78
msgid ""
"If customers are allowed to pay when picking up their order in stores or by "
"wire transfer, the quotation is **not** be confirmed and the stock is "
"**not** be reserved. Orders must be confirmed manually to reserve products "
"in stock."
msgstr ""
"Si les clients sont autorisés à payer lors du retrait de leur commande en "
"boutique ou par virement bancaire, le devis n'est **pas** confirmé et le "
"stock n'est **pas** réservé. Les commandes doivent être confirmées "
"manuellement pour réserver des produits en stock."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:83
msgid ""
":doc:`../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/invoicing`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/invoicing`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:84
msgid ""
":doc:`../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/labels`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/labels`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:85
msgid ""
":doc:`../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/multipack`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/multipack`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:88
msgid "Returns and refunds"
msgstr "Retours et remboursements"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:90
msgid ""
"Customers can only return an order through an online form. It may not be "
"possible to return products depending on the return strategy or type of "
"product."
msgstr ""
"Les clients ne peuvent retourner une commande que par l'intermédiaire d'un "
"formulaire en ligne. Il se peut qu'il ne soit pas possible de retourner des "
"produits en fonction de la stratégie de retour ou du type de produit."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:93
msgid ""
"Full refunds can be directly sent to customers from within the order "
"interface. A refund-compatible payment provider needs to be enabled first."
msgstr ""
"Les remboursements intégraux peuvent être envoyés directement aux clients à "
"partir de l'interface de commande. Un fournisseur de paiement compatible "
"avec les remboursements doit d'abord être activé."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:97
msgid ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:98
msgid ":doc:`/applications/services/helpdesk/advanced/after_sales`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/services/helpdesk/advanced/after_sales`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:99
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/payment_providers`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/payment_providers`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:104
msgid "Invoice and legal requirements"
msgstr "Facture et exigences légales"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:106
msgid ""
"The final step of an ecommerce order is to generate the invoice and send it "
"to the customer. Depending on your needs, an invoice can either be generated "
"automatically or on demand of the customer. This process can be automated if "
"(and when) the online payment is :ref:`confirmed <handling/sales>`."
msgstr ""
"La dernière étape d'une commande eCommerce consiste à générer la facture et "
"à l'envoyer au client. Selon vos besoins, une facture peut être générée "
"automatiquement ou à la demande du client. Ce processus peut être automatisé "
"si (et quand) le paiement en ligne est :ref:`confirmé <handling/sales>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:111
msgid ""
"To automate invoicing, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings` and in the :guilabel:`Invoicing` section, "
"enable :guilabel:`Automatic Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Pour automatiser la facturation, allez à :menuselection:`Site Web --> "
"Configuration --> Paramètres` et dans la section :guilabel:`Facturation`, "
"activez la fonctionnalité :guilabel:`Facture automatique`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:3
msgid "Payment providers"
msgstr "Fournisseurs de paiement"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo supports a multitude of online :doc:`payment providers </applications/"
"finance/payment_providers>` for your website, allowing your customers to pay "
"with their preferred payment methods."
msgstr ""
"Odoo prend en charge une multitude de :doc:`fournisseurs de paiement </"
"applications/finance/payment_providers>` en ligne pour votre site web, "
"permettant à vos clients de payer avec leur mode de paiement préféré."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:10
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:54
msgid ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:11
msgid ":doc:`checkout`"
msgstr ":doc:`paiement`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:14
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website.rst:28
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration.rst:5
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:21
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/reporting/link_tracker.rst:10
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Configuration"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:16
msgid ""
"To set up payment providers on the eCommerce app, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Payment Providers`. From "
"here, :guilabel:`Activate` the payment providers you wish to have available "
"on your shop, and configure them according to your needs."
msgstr ""
"Pour configurer des fournisseurs de paiement sur l'application eCommerce, "
"allez à :menuselection:`Site Web --> Configuration --> Fournisseurs de "
"paiement`. De là, :guilabel:`activez` les fournisseurs de paiement que vous "
"voulez rendre disponible sur votre boutique et configurez-les en fonction de "
"vos besoins."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:20
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can access **payment providers** "
"via :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Shop - Payment` section, you can :guilabel:`Configure SEPA "
"Direct Debit` if you wish to use it, as well as :guilabel:`View other "
"providers`. If you use the :guilabel:`Authorize.net` payment provider, "
"the :ref:`Payment Capture Method <payment_providers/manual_capture>` can be "
"configured in that same menu."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez également accéder aux **fournisseurs de paiement** "
"via :menuselection:`Site Web --> Configuration --> Paramètres`. Dans la "
"section :guilabel:`Boutique - Paiement`, vous pouvez :guilabel:`Configurer "
"le prélèvement SEPA` si vous souhaitez l'utiliser et :guilabel:`Voir les "
"autres fournisseurs`. Si vous utiliser le fournisseur de "
"paiement :guilabel:`Authorize.net`, la :ref:`Méthode de capture de paiements "
"<payment_providers/manual_capture>` peut être configurée dans ce même menu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:26
msgid ""
"If you are using :doc:`/applications/finance/payment_providers/paypal`, you "
"can also enable and configure it here."
msgstr ""
"Si vous utilisez :doc:`/applications/finance/payment_providers/paypal`, vous "
"pouvez également l'activer et le configurer ici."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:30
msgid "Checkout payment options"
msgstr "Options de paiement"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:32
msgid ""
"Once activated, customers can choose the payment provider of their choice "
"during the **checkout process**, at the :guilabel:`Confirm Order` step."
msgstr ""
"Une fois activé, les clients peuvent choisir le fournisseur de paiement de "
"leur choix pendant le **processus de paiement**, à "
"l'étape :guilabel:`Confirmer la commande`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:None
msgid "Payment provider selection at checkout"
msgstr "Sélection du fournisseur de paiement lors du paiement"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:40
msgid "eWallets and gift cards"
msgstr "E-wallets et cartes-cadeaux"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:42
msgid ""
"When checking out, customers can pay with an eWallet or gift cards. To "
"enable these, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, "
"and in the :guilabel:`Shop-Products` section, "
"enable :menuselection:`Discounts, Loyalty & Gift Card`."
msgstr ""
"Lors du passage en caisse, les clients peuvent payer avec des e-wallets ou "
"des cartes-cadeaux. Pour les activer, allez à :menuselection:`Site Web --> "
"Configuration --> Paramètres` et dans la section :guilabel:`Boutique - "
"Produits` activez :menuselection:`Remises, Fidélité & Cartes-cadeaux`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:46
msgid ""
"Once enabled, customers can enter their gift card **code** or pay with their "
"eWallet at the checkout step."
msgstr ""
"Une fois cette option activée, les clients peuvent saisir le **code** de "
"leur carte-cadeau ou payer avec leur e-wallet à l'étape du passage en caisse."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:None
msgid "Enter gift card code to process checkout"
msgstr "Saisissez le code de la carte-cadeau pour procéder au paiement."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:3
msgid "Performance management"
msgstr "Gestion des performances"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo integrates a variety of tools to analyze and improve the performance of "
"your eCommerce website."
msgstr ""
"Odoo intègre une variété d'outils pour analyser et améliorer la performance "
"de votre site d'eCommerce."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:9
msgid "Data monitoring"
msgstr "Suivi des données"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:11
msgid ""
"**Website** allows monitoring and analysis of the sales performance of your "
"eCommerce. To access the **reporting view**, go to :menuselection:`Website --"
"> Reporting --> eCommerce`. This dashboard helps you monitor everything "
"related to sales, such as sales performance per product, category, day, etc."
msgstr ""
"**Site Web** vous permet de suivre et d'analyser les performances de vente "
"de votre eCommerce. Pour accéder à la **vue d'analyse**, allez "
"à :menuselection:`Site Web --> Analyse --> eCommerce`. Ce tableau de bord "
"vous aide à surveiller tout ce qui concerne les ventes, comme les "
"performances de vente par produit, catégorie, jour, etc."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:None
msgid "Performance reporting of eCommerce"
msgstr "Analyse des performances d'eCommerce"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:19
msgid ""
"By clicking :guilabel:`Measures`, you can select the type of measurement "
"used, such as:"
msgstr ""
"En cliquant sur :guilabel:`Mesures`, vous pouvez sélectionner le type de "
"mesure utilisé :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:21
msgid ":guilabel:`Margin`;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Marge` ;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:22
msgid ":guilabel:`Qty Invoiced`;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Qté facturée` ;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:23
msgid ":guilabel:`Untaxed Total`;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Total hors taxes` ;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:24
msgid ":guilabel:`Volume`;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Volume` ;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:25
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:27
msgid ""
"Other options include **multiple views (Pivot, etc.), comparison** by "
"periods or years, and directly :guilabel:`insert in spreadsheet`, etc."
msgstr ""
"D'autres options incluent **vues multiples (tableau croisé dynamique, etc.), "
"comparaison** par période ou année et directement :guilabel:`insérer dans "
"feuille de calcul`, etc."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:31
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:147
msgid "Analytics"
msgstr "Analytique"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:33
msgid ""
"It is possible to link your Odoo website with :ref:`analytics/plausible` "
"and :ref:`analytics/google-analytics`."
msgstr ""
"Il est possible de lier votre site web d'Odoo avec :ref:`analytics/"
"plausible` et :ref:`analytics/google-analytics`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:39
msgid "Email queue optimization"
msgstr "Optimisation de la file d'attente des emails"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:41
msgid ""
"For websites handling flash sales (e.g., event ticket sales) or experiencing "
"high traffic spikes, order confirmation emails can become a performance "
"bottleneck, potentially slowing down the checkout process for other "
"customers."
msgstr ""
"Pour les sites web gérant des ventes flash (ex. : vente de billets "
"d'événements) ou connaissant des pics de trafic élevés, les emails de "
"confirmation de commande peuvent devenir un goulot d'étranglement de "
"performance, ralentissant potentiellement le processus de paiement pour les "
"autres clients."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:45
msgid ""
"To improve performance, these emails can be queued and processed separately "
"from the order confirmation flow. This is managed by the :guilabel:`Sales: "
"Send pending emails` scheduled action, which sends queued emails as soon as "
"possible."
msgstr ""
"Pour améliorer les performances, ces emails peuvent être mis en file "
"d'attente et traités séparément du flux de confirmation de commande. Cela "
"est géré par l'action planifiée :guilabel:`Ventes : Envoyer les emails en "
"attente`, qui envoie les emails en file d'attente dès que possible."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:49
msgid "To enable asynchronous email sending:"
msgstr "Pour activer l'envoi asynchrone des emails :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:51
msgid ""
"Enable the :doc:`developer mode </applications/general/developer_mode>`."
msgstr ""
"Activer le :doc:`mode développeur </applications/general/developer_mode>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:52
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Apps`, remove the :guilabel:`Apps` filter, and install "
"the :guilabel:`Sales - Async Emails` module."
msgstr ""
"Aller à :menuselection:`Applications`, retirer le filtre "
":guilabel:`Applications`, et installer le module :guilabel:`Ventes - Emails "
"asynchrones`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:54
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> System Parameters` and set "
"the :guilabel:`sale.async_emails` system parameter to `True`."
msgstr ""
"Aller à :menuselection:`Paramètres --> Technique --> Paramètres système` et "
"définir le paramètre système :guilabel:`sale.async_emails` sur `True`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:56
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> Scheduled Actions` and "
"ensure that the :guilabel:`Sales: Send pending emails` scheduled action is "
"enabled."
msgstr ""
"Aller à :menuselection:`Paramètres --> Technique --> Actions planifiées` et "
"s'assurer que l'action planifiée :guilabel:`Ventes : Envoyer les emails en "
"attente` est activée."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:60
msgid ""
"Enabling this feature may delay order confirmation and invoice emails by a "
"few minutes. It is recommended only for high-traffic websites, as it can "
"introduce unnecessary delays for e-commerce websites with moderate traffic."
msgstr ""
"Activer cette fonctionnalité peut retarder les emails de confirmation de "
"commande et de facturation de quelques minutes. Elle est recommandée "
"uniquement pour les sites Web à fort trafic, car elle peut introduire des "
"retards inutiles pour les sites eCommerce à trafic modéré."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:5
msgid "Products"
msgstr "Produits"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:7
msgid ""
"**Odoo eCommerce** allows you to :ref:`add products <ecommerce/products/add-"
"products>` and manage your :ref:`product pages <ecommerce/products/product-"
"page>` directly from the Website app. It also allows you to "
"add :ref:`product variants <ecommerce/products/product-variants>` "
"and :ref:`digital files <ecommerce/products/digital-"
"files>`, :ref:`translating <ecommerce/products/translation>` the product "
"page content, :ref:`managing stock <ecommerce/products/stock-management>`, "
"and enabling :ref:`product comparisons <ecommerce/products/product-"
"comparison>`."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo eCommerce** permet d':ref:`ajouter des produits <ecommerce/products/"
"add-products>` et de gérer vos :ref:`pages produit <ecommerce/products/"
"product-page>` directement depuis l'application Site Web. Il permet "
"également d'ajouter des :ref:`variantes de produit <ecommerce/products/"
"product-variants>` et des :ref:`fichiers numériques <ecommerce/products/"
"digital-files>`, de :ref:`traduire <ecommerce/products/translation>` le "
"contenu de la page produit, de :ref:`gérer le stock <ecommerce/products/"
"stock-management>`, et d'activer les :ref:`comparaisons de produits "
"<ecommerce/products/product-comparison>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:18
msgid "Add products"
msgstr "Ajoutez des produits"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:23
msgid "Create products"
msgstr "Créez des produits"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:25
msgid ""
"To create a product from the frontend, click :guilabel:`+ New` in the top-"
"right corner, then :guilabel:`Product`. Enter the :guilabel:`Product "
"Name`, :guilabel:`Sales Price`, the default :guilabel:`Customer Taxes` for "
"local transactions, and :guilabel:`Save`. You can then update the product's "
"details, add an image, and :ref:`customize <ecommerce/products/"
"customization>` the product page. When you :guilabel:`Save`, the product "
"page is automatically published."
msgstr ""
"Pour créer un produit depuis le frontend, cliquer sur :guilabel:`+ Nouveau` "
"dans le coin supérieur droit, puis sur :guilabel:`Produit`. Saisir le "
":guilabel:`Nom du produit`, le :guilabel:`Prix de vente`, les "
":guilabel:`Taxes clients` par défaut pour les transactions locales, et "
":guilabel:`Enregistrer`. Vous pouvez ensuite mettre à jour les détails du "
"produit, ajouter une image, et :ref:`personnaliser <ecommerce/products/"
"customization>` la page produit. Lorsque vous :guilabel:`Enregistrez`, la "
"page produit est automatiquement publiée."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:32
msgid ""
"You can also create a product from the backend by going "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products` and "
"clicking :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez également créer un produit depuis le backend en allant à "
":menuselection:`Site Web --> eCommerce --> Produits` et en cliquant sur "
":guilabel:`Nouveau`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:34
msgid ""
"Products created from the frontend are automatically :ref:`published "
"<website/pages/un-publish-page>`, while products created from the backend "
"are not. To publish a product, click the :guilabel:`Go to Website` smart "
"button to access the product page, then toggle the switch "
"from :guilabel:`Unpublished` to :guilabel:`Published`."
msgstr ""
"Les produits créés depuis le frontend sont automatiquement :ref:`publiés "
"<website/pages/un-publish-page>`, tandis que les produits créés depuis le "
"backend ne le sont pas. Pour publier un produit, cliquer sur le bouton "
"intelligent :guilabel:`Aller au site Web` pour accéder à la page produit, "
"puis basculer l'interrupteur de :guilabel:`Non publié` à :guilabel:`Publié`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:40
msgid ""
":doc:`Create new products using the Barcode Lookup database </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/barcode/setup/barcodelookup>`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Créer de nouveaux produits en utilisant la base de données de "
"recherche de codes-barres </applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/setup/"
"barcodelookup>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:46
msgid "Import products"
msgstr "Importer des produits"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:48
msgid ""
"To :ref:`import product data <essentials/export_import_data/import-data>` "
"using XLSX or CSV files, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> "
"Products`, click the :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`gear`) icon, "
"then :ref:`Import records <essentials/export_import_data/import-data>`."
msgstr ""
"Pour :ref:`importer des données produit <essentials/export_import_data/"
"import-data>` à l'aide de fichiers XLSX ou CSV, aller à :menuselection:`Site "
"Web --> eCommerce --> Produits`, cliquer sur l'icône :icon:`fa-cog` "
"(:guilabel:`engrenage`), puis sur :ref:`Importer des enregistrements "
"<essentials/export_import_data/import-data>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:53
msgid "To publish **large batches** of products, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Pour publier des **lots importants** de produits, suivre ces étapes :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:55
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products`."
msgstr "Aller à :menuselection:`Site Web --> eCommerce --> Produits`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:56
msgid ""
"Remove the :guilabel:`Published` filter and switch to the :guilabel:`List` "
"view."
msgstr ""
"Retirer le filtre :guilabel:`Publié` et passer à la vue :guilabel:`Liste`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:57
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-sliders` (:guilabel:`dropdown toggle`) icon and "
"enable :guilabel:`Is published`."
msgstr ""
"Cliquer sur l'icône :icon:`fa-sliders` (:guilabel:`bascule de liste "
"déroulante`) et activer :guilabel:`Est publié`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:59
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Is Published` column to re-order it by **published** or "
"**unpublished** products."
msgstr ""
"Cliquer sur la colonne :guilabel:`Est publié` pour la réordonner par "
"produits **publiés** ou **non publiés**."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:61
msgid "Select the products to publish by ticking their box."
msgstr "Sélectionner les produits à publier en cochant leur case."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:62
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Is Published` column, tick the box for any of the selected "
"products, then :guilabel:`Confirm` to publish them."
msgstr ""
"Dans la colonne :guilabel:`Est publié`, cocher la case pour l'un des "
"produits sélectionnés, puis :guilabel:`Confirmer` pour les publier."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:68
msgid "Product page customization"
msgstr "Personnalisation de la page produit"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:73
msgid "Product information"
msgstr "Informations sur le produit"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:76
msgid ""
"To add general information about a product, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products` and select the "
"product. You can configure the product page from the form by "
"adding :ref:`variants <ecommerce/products/product-variants>`, :ref:`digital "
"documents <ecommerce/products/digital-files>`, or :ref:`translating "
"<ecommerce/products/translation>` content."
msgstr ""
"Pour ajouter des informations générales sur un produit, aller à "
":menuselection:`Site Web --> eCommerce --> Produits` et sélectionner le "
"produit. Vous pouvez configurer la page produit depuis le formulaire en "
"ajoutant des :ref:`variantes <ecommerce/products/product-variants>`, des "
":ref:`documents numériques <ecommerce/products/digital-files>` ou en "
":ref:`traduisant <ecommerce/products/translation>` le contenu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:81
msgid ""
"You can also add an ecommerce-specific product description to be displayed "
"below the product name on the product's page. To do so, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Ecommerce "
"description` section, and add a description. Use Odoo's :doc:`rich-text "
"editor <../../essentials/html_editor>` features to personalize the content."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez également ajouter une description de produit spécifique à "
"l'ecommerce à afficher sous le nom du produit sur la page du produit. Pour "
"ce faire, aller à l'onglet :guilabel:`Ventes`, descendre jusqu'à la section "
":guilabel:`Description ecommerce` et ajouter une description. Utiliser les "
"fonctionnalités de l':doc:`éditeur de texte enrichi <../../essentials/"
"html_editor>` d'Odoo pour personnaliser le contenu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:87
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Go to Website` smart button to return to the frontend "
"product's page."
msgstr ""
"Cliquer sur le bouton intelligent :guilabel:`Aller au site Web` pour "
"retourner à la page produit du frontend."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:92
msgid "Product presentation"
msgstr "Présentation du produit"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:94
msgid ""
"To customize the product presentation on the website, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Shop` and click on the product. Click :guilabel:`Edit` "
"to :ref:`customize <ecommerce/products/customization>` the page, :ref:`edit "
"its images <ecommerce/products/image-customization>` or add :doc:`building "
"blocks <../../websites/website/web_design/building_blocks>`."
msgstr ""
"Pour personnaliser la présentation du produit sur le site Web, aller à la "
":guilabel:`Boutique` et cliquer sur le produit. Cliquer sur "
":guilabel:`Modifier` pour :ref:`personnaliser <ecommerce/products/"
"customization>` la page, :ref:`modifier ses images <ecommerce/products/image-"
"customization>` ou ajouter des :doc:`blocs de construction <../../websites/"
"website/web_design/building_blocks>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:100
msgid ""
"When dragging and dropping a building block on the product page, placing it "
"above or below the top or bottom blue lines makes it visible on all product "
"pages."
msgstr ""
"Lors du glisser-déposer d'un bloc de construction sur la page produit, le "
"placer au-dessus ou en dessous des lignes bleues supérieure ou inférieure le "
"rend visible sur toutes les pages produit."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:102
msgid ""
"You can edit any text on your website by clicking on it while "
"in :guilabel:`Edit` mode."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez modifier n'importe quel texte sur votre site Web en cliquant "
"dessus en mode :guilabel:`Modifier`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:104
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Customize` tab to modify the page layout or add features:"
msgstr ""
"Utiliser l'onglet :guilabel:`Personnaliser` pour modifier la mise en page ou "
"ajouter des fonctionnalités :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:106
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Terms and Conditions`: Toggle the switch to display a link to "
"your :doc:`terms and conditions <../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices/"
"terms_conditions>` on the product page."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Conditions générales` : activer l'interrupteur pour afficher un "
"lien vers vos :doc:`conditions générales <../../finance/accounting/"
"customer_invoices/terms_conditions>` sur la page produit."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:110
msgid ":guilabel:`Customers`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Clients` :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:112
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Rating`: Allow logged-in portal users to submit product reviews "
"by clicking the stars below the product's name and sharing their experience "
"in the :guilabel:`Customer Reviews` section at the bottom. Reviews are "
"visible from the product page using the :icon:`fa-plus` (:guilabel:`plus`) "
"icon next to the :guilabel:`Customer Reviews` heading or from the product "
"form's chatter. To restrict visibility to internal employees, toggle "
"the :guilabel:`Public` switch next to the review comment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Évaluation` : permettre aux utilisateurs du portail connectés de "
"soumettre des avis produit en cliquant sur les étoiles sous le nom du "
"produit et en partageant leur expérience dans la section :guilabel:`Avis "
"clients` en bas. Les avis sont visibles depuis la page produit en utilisant "
"l'icône :icon:`fa-plus` (:guilabel:`plus`) à côté du titre :guilabel:`Avis "
"clients` ou depuis le chatter du formulaire produit. Pour restreindre la "
"visibilité aux employés internes, activer l'interrupteur :guilabel:`Public` "
"à côté du commentaire d'avis."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:118
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Share`: Add social media and email icon buttons allowing "
"customers to share the product through those channels."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Partager` : ajouter des boutons d'icônes de réseaux sociaux et "
"d'e-mail permettant aux clients de partager le produit via ces canaux."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:121
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Select Quantity`: Toggle the switch to allow customers to select "
"the product quantity they want to purchase."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sélectionner la quantité` : activer l'interrupteur pour permettre "
"aux clients de sélectionner la quantité de produit qu'ils souhaitent acheter."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:124
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tax Indication`: Toggle the switch to indicate if the price "
"is :ref:`VAT included or excluded <ecommerce/prices/taxes>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:127
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Variants`: Show all possible product :ref:`variants <ecommerce/"
"products/product-variants>` vertically as a :guilabel:`Products List` or "
"horizontally as selectable :guilabel:`Options` to compose the variant "
"yourself."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Variantes` : afficher toutes les :ref:`variantes <ecommerce/"
"products/product-variants>` de produit possibles verticalement sous forme de "
":guilabel:`Liste de produits` ou horizontalement sous forme "
"d':guilabel:`Options` sélectionnables pour composer vous-même la variante."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:131
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Tags`: Toggle the switch to display "
"the :guilabel:`Product Template Tags` on the product page and allow "
"customers to filter products using those tags."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tags de produit` : activer l'interrupteur pour afficher les "
":guilabel:`Tags de modèle de produit` sur la page produit et permettre aux "
"clients de filtrer les produits en utilisant ces tags."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:134
msgid ":guilabel:`Cart`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Panier` :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:136
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Buy Now`: Add a :icon:`fa-bolt` :guilabel:`Buy Now` option to "
"take the customer to the checkout page."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Acheter maintenant` : ajouter une option :icon:`fa-bolt` "
":guilabel:`Acheter maintenant` pour diriger le client vers la page de "
"paiement."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:138
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wishlist`: Add an :icon:`fa-heart-o` :guilabel:`Add to wishlist` "
"option allowing logged-in customers to save products in a wishlist."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Liste de souhaits` : Ajouter une option :icon:`fa-heart-o` "
":guilabel:`Ajouter à la liste de souhaits` permettant aux clients connectés "
"d'enregistrer des produits dans une liste de souhaits."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:140
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Compare`: Add a :icon:`fa-exchange` :guilabel:`Compare` option, "
"allowing customers to :ref:`compare products <ecommerce/products/product-"
"comparison>` based on their attributes."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Comparer` : Ajouter une option :icon:`fa-exchange` "
":guilabel:`Comparer`, permettant aux clients de :ref:`comparer des produits "
"<ecommerce/products/product-comparison>` en fonction de leurs attributs."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:143
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Specification`: Select :guilabel:`Bottom of Page` to display a "
"detailed list of the attributes and their values available for the product. "
"This option only works for products with :ref:`variants <ecommerce/products/"
"product-variants>` if the :ref:`Product comparison tool <ecommerce/products/"
"product-comparison>` is enabled in the Website :guilabel:`Settings`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Spécification` : Sélectionner :guilabel:`Bas de page` pour "
"afficher une liste détaillée des attributs et de leurs valeurs disponibles "
"pour le produit. Cette option ne fonctionne pour les produits avec "
":ref:`variantes <ecommerce/products/product-variants>` que si l':ref:`Outil "
"de comparaison de produits <ecommerce/products/product-comparison>` est "
"activé dans les :guilabel:`Paramètres` du Site Web."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:150
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Variants`, :icon:`fa-heart-o` :guilabel:`Wishlist`, and :icon:`fa-"
"exchange` :guilabel:`Compare` options must be enabled by going "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, in "
"the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section."
msgstr ""
"Les options :guilabel:`Variantes`, :icon:`fa-heart-o` :guilabel:`Liste de "
"souhaits`, et :icon:`fa-exchange` :guilabel:`Comparer` doivent être activées "
"en allant dans :menuselection:`Site Web --> Configuration --> Paramètres`, "
"dans la section :guilabel:`Boutique - Produits`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:154
msgid "Enabled functions apply to all product pages."
msgstr "Les fonctions activées s'appliquent à toutes les pages de produits."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:155
msgid ""
"Products with single values for their attributes do not generate variants "
"but are still displayed in the :guilabel:`Product Specifications`."
msgstr ""
"Les produits avec des valeurs uniques pour leurs attributs ne génèrent pas "
"de variantes mais sont toujours affichés dans les :guilabel:`Spécifications "
"du produit`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:161
msgid "Product images and videos"
msgstr "Images et vidéos de produits"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:163
msgid ""
"To add more media items, such as images and videos, navigate to "
"the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/products/product-form>`, then go to "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` tab and click :guilabel:`Add Media` under "
"the :guilabel:`Ecommerce Media` section. In the :guilabel:`Select a media` "
"pop-up window, go to the :guilabel:`Images` tab, select an image, "
"click :guilabel:`Upload an image` or :guilabel:`Add URL`. Or navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Videos` tab, paste a video URL or embed code. Once done, "
"click :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr ""
"Pour ajouter davantage d'éléments multimédias, tels que des images et des "
"vidéos, accéder au :ref:`formulaire du produit <ecommerce/products/product-"
"form>`, puis aller dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Ventes` et cliquer sur "
":guilabel:`Ajouter un média` sous la section :guilabel:`Média eCommerce`. "
"Dans la fenêtre contextuelle :guilabel:`Sélectionner un média`, aller dans "
"l'onglet :guilabel:`Images`, sélectionner une image, cliquer sur "
":guilabel:`Télécharger une image` ou :guilabel:`Ajouter une URL`. Ou accéder "
"à l'onglet :guilabel:`Vidéos`, coller une URL de vidéo ou un code "
"d'intégration. Une fois terminé, cliquer sur :guilabel:`Ajouter`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:170
msgid ""
"To customize the images or videos, go to the ecommerce product page, "
"click :guilabel:`Edit` and select the relevant media. In "
"the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, use the following features:"
msgstr ""
"Pour personnaliser les images ou les vidéos, aller sur la page du produit "
"eCommerce, cliquer sur :guilabel:`Modifier` et sélectionner le média "
"concerné. Dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Personnaliser`, utiliser les "
"fonctionnalités suivantes :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:173
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Images Width`: Changes the width of the product images displayed "
"on the page."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Largeur des images` : Modifier la largeur des images de produits "
"affichées sur la page."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:174
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Layout`: The :guilabel:`Carousel` layout allows customers to "
"navigate from one image to the next using the :icon:`fa-angle-left` "
"(:guilabel:`left arrow`) or :icon:`fa-angle-right` (:guilabel:`right "
"arrow`); whereas the :guilabel:`Grid` displays four images in a square "
"layout."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Disposition` : La disposition :guilabel:`Carrousel` permet aux "
"clients de naviguer d'une image à l'autre en utilisant le :icon:`fa-angle-"
"left` (:guilabel:`flèche gauche`) ou le :icon:`fa-angle-right` "
"(:guilabel:`flèche droite`) ; tandis que la :guilabel:`Grille` affiche "
"quatre images dans une disposition carrée."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:177
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Image Zoom`: Select the zoom effect for product "
"images: :guilabel:`Magnifier on hover` :guilabel:`Pop-up on "
"Click`, :guilabel:`Both`, or :guilabel:`None`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Zoom d'image` : Sélectionner l'effet de zoom pour les images de "
"produits : :guilabel:`Loupe au survol`, :guilabel:`Pop-up au clic`, "
":guilabel:`Les deux`, ou :guilabel:`Aucun`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:179
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Thumbnails`: Align thumbnails on the :icon:`fa-long-arrow-left` "
"(:guilabel:`Left`) or at the :icon:`fa-long-arrow-down` (:guilabel:`Bottom`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vignettes` : Aligner les vignettes sur le :icon:`fa-long-arrow-"
"left` (:guilabel:`Gauche`) ou en :icon:`fa-long-arrow-down` (:guilabel:`Bas`)"
"."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:182
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Main Image`: Click :guilabel:`Replace` to change the product's "
"main image."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Image principale` : Cliquer sur :guilabel:`Remplacer` pour "
"changer l'image principale du produit."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:183
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Extra Images`: :guilabel:`Add` more extra images or videos "
"(including via URL) or :guilabel:`Remove all`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Images supplémentaires` : :guilabel:`Ajouter` davantage d'images "
"ou de vidéos supplémentaires (y compris via URL) ou :guilabel:`Tout "
"supprimer`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:187
msgid ""
"Images must be in PNG or JPG format, with at least one dimension (height or "
"width) greater than 1024 pixels to trigger the zoom."
msgstr ""
"Les images doivent être au format PNG ou JPG, avec au moins une dimension "
"(hauteur ou largeur) supérieure à 1024 pixels pour déclencher le zoom."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:193
msgid "Products block"
msgstr "Bloc de produits"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:195
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Products` :doc:`building block <../website/web_design/"
"building_blocks>` is used to display a selection of products sold on your "
"website."
msgstr ""
"Le :guilabel:`bloc de construction` :doc:`Produits <../website/web_design/"
"building_blocks>` est utilisé pour afficher une sélection de produits vendus "
"sur votre site web."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:None
msgid "Example of a products block"
msgstr "Exemple d'un bloc de produits"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:201
msgid ""
"By default, the block displays the :guilabel:`Newest Products`. To change "
"which products are shown, go to the :guilabel:`Customize` "
"tab's :guilabel:`Products` section and set the :guilabel:`Filter` field "
"to :guilabel:`Recently Sold Products` or :guilabel:`Recently Viewed "
"Products`."
msgstr ""
"Par défaut, le bloc affiche les :guilabel:`Produits les plus récents`. Pour "
"modifier les produits affichés, aller dans la section :guilabel:`Produits` "
"de l'onglet :guilabel:`Personnaliser` et définir le champ :guilabel:`Filtre` "
"sur :guilabel:`Produits récemment vendus` ou :guilabel:`Produits récemment "
"consultés`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:205
msgid ""
"In addition, it is possible to display products from a specific category "
"only using the :guilabel:`Category` field."
msgstr ""
"De plus, il est possible d'afficher des produits d'une catégorie spécifique "
"uniquement en utilisant le champ :guilabel:`Catégorie`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:208
msgid ""
"You can also filter products by :guilabel:`Tags`, "
"include :guilabel:`Variants`, and adjust the display by selecting a "
"different :guilabel:`Template`."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez également filtrer les produits par :guilabel:`Étiquettes`, "
"inclure les :guilabel:`Variantes`, et ajuster l'affichage en sélectionnant "
"un :guilabel:`Modèle` différent."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:214
msgid "Product variants"
msgstr "Variantes de produit"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:216
msgid ""
":doc:`Product variants <../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/"
"variants>` are different versions of the same product, such as various "
"colors or materials, with potential differences in price and availability."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Variantes de produit <../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/"
"variants>` sont différentes versions d'un même produit, comme diverses "
"couleurs ou matériaux, avec des différences potentielles de prix et de "
"disponibilité."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:220
msgid "To configure product variants for a product:"
msgstr "Pour configurer les variantes de produit pour un produit :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:222
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:104
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:26
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:136
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr "Allez à :menuselection:`Site Web --> Configuration --> Paramètres`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:223
msgid ""
"Scroll down to the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section and enable "
"the :guilabel:`Product Variants` feature."
msgstr ""
"Défiler jusqu'à la section :guilabel:`Boutique - Produits` et activer la "
"fonctionnalité :guilabel:`Variantes de produit`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:225
msgid ""
"Access the :ref:`product forms <ecommerce/products/product-form>` and go to "
"the :guilabel:`Attributes & Variants` tab, where you can add attributes and "
"values, allowing customers to configure and select product variants on the "
"product page. For multiple attributes, you can combine them to create "
"specific variants."
msgstr ""
"Accéder aux :ref:`formulaires de produit <ecommerce/products/product-form>` "
"et aller dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Attributs & Variantes`, où vous pouvez "
"ajouter des attributs et des valeurs, permettant aux clients de configurer "
"et sélectionner des variantes de produit sur la page produit. Pour plusieurs "
"attributs, vous pouvez les combiner pour créer des variantes spécifiques."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:230
msgid ""
"To display or hide an attribute on the :guilabel:`Shop` page and allow "
"visitors to filter them, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> "
"Attributes`, click on the attribute, and select :guilabel:`Visible` "
"or :guilabel:`Hidden` in the :guilabel:`eCommerce Filter Visibility` field."
msgstr ""
"Pour afficher ou masquer un attribut sur la page :guilabel:`Boutique` et "
"permettre aux visiteurs de les filtrer, aller dans :menuselection:`Site "
"Web --> eCommerce --> Attributs`, cliquer sur l'attribut, et sélectionner "
":guilabel:`Visible` ou :guilabel:`Masqué` dans le champ "
":guilabel:`Visibilité du filtre eCommerce`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:235
msgid ""
"To display the product attributes in the :doc:`product catalog <products/"
"catalog>`, set the :guilabel:`Attributes` feature to :guilabel:`Left` using "
"the website editor."
msgstr ""
"Pour afficher les attributs de produit dans le :doc:`catalogue de produits "
"<products/catalog>`, définissez la fonctionnalité :guilabel:`Attributs` sur "
":guilabel:`Gauche` à l'aide de l'éditeur de Site Web."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:237
msgid ""
"To group attributes under the same section when :ref:`comparing products "
"<ecommerce/products/product-comparison>`, go to the :guilabel:`eCommerce "
"Category` field and either select an :doc:`existing category or create a new "
"one <../../websites/ecommerce/products>`."
msgstr ""
"Pour regrouper les attributs sous la même section lors de la "
":ref:`comparaison de produits <ecommerce/products/product-comparison>`, "
"aller dans le champ :guilabel:`Catégorie eCommerce` et soit sélectionner une "
":doc:`catégorie existante ou en créer une nouvelle <../../websites/ecommerce/"
"products>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:243
msgid "Two attribute values are needed to make the filter visible."
msgstr "Deux valeurs d'attribut sont nécessaires pour rendre le filtre visible."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:246
msgid ""
":doc:`Product variants <../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Variantes de produit <../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/"
"variants>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:251
msgid "Digital files"
msgstr "Fichiers numériques"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:253
msgid ""
"You can link digital files like certificates, eBooks, or user manuals to the "
"products. These documents are available :ref:`before payment <ecommerce-"
"products-digital-files-before-payment>` on the product page or in the "
"customer portal :ref:`after checkout <ecommerce-products-digital-files-after-"
"payment>`."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez lier des fichiers numériques tels que des certificats, des "
"livres électroniques ou des manuels d'utilisation aux produits. Ces "
"documents sont disponibles :ref:`avant le paiement <ecommerce-products-"
"digital-files-before-payment>` sur la page produit ou dans le portail client "
":ref:`après le paiement <ecommerce-products-digital-files-after-payment>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:258
msgid ""
"To link a digital file to a product, go to the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/"
"products/product-form>` and click the :guilabel:`Documents` smart button. "
"Then, click :guilabel:`Upload` to upload a file directly, or for additional "
"options, click :guilabel:`New`, then :guilabel:`Upload your file`."
msgstr ""
"Pour lier un fichier numérique à un produit, aller dans le :ref:`formulaire "
"de produit <ecommerce/products/product-form>` et cliquer sur le bouton "
"intelligent :guilabel:`Documents`. Ensuite, cliquer sur "
":guilabel:`Téléverser` pour téléverser un fichier directement, ou pour des "
"options supplémentaires, cliquer sur :guilabel:`Nouveau`, puis "
":guilabel:`Téléverser votre fichier`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:263
msgid ""
"You can link a URL instead of a digital file. To do so, "
"click :guilabel:`New`, go to the :guilabel:`Type` field, and "
"select :guilabel:`URL`."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez lier une URL au lieu d'un fichier numérique. Pour ce faire, "
"cliquer sur :guilabel:`Nouveau`, aller dans le champ :guilabel:`Type`, et "
"sélectionner :guilabel:`URL`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:265
msgid ""
"To edit an existing file, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
"(:guilabel:`dropdown menu`) in the top-right corner of the document card and "
"click :guilabel:`Edit`."
msgstr ""
"Pour modifier un fichier existant, cliquer sur :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
"(:guilabel:`menu déroulant`) dans le coin supérieur droit de la carte du "
"document et cliquer sur :guilabel:`Modifier`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:271
msgid "Digital files available before payment"
msgstr "Fichiers numériques disponibles avant le paiement"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:273
msgid ""
"To make the file available on the product page (before payment), leave "
"the :guilabel:`Visibility` field blank and toggle the :guilabel:`Show on "
"product page` switch."
msgstr ""
"Pour rendre le fichier disponible sur la page produit (avant le paiement), "
"laisser le champ :guilabel:`Visibilité` vide et activer le bouton "
":guilabel:`Afficher sur la page produit`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:None
msgid "digital file available before payment on the  product page"
msgstr "fichier numérique disponible avant le paiement sur la page produit"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:282
msgid "Digital files available after payment"
msgstr "Fichiers numériques disponibles après le paiement"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:284
msgid ""
"To make the file available (after payment), set the :guilabel:`Visibility` "
"field to :guilabel:`Confirmed order` and turn off the :guilabel:`Show on "
"product page` switch."
msgstr ""
"Pour rendre le fichier disponible (après le paiement), définir le champ "
":guilabel:`Visibilité` sur :guilabel:`Commande confirmée` et désactiver le "
"bouton :guilabel:`Afficher sur la page produit`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:290
msgid "Translation"
msgstr "Traduction"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:292
msgid ""
"If multiple languages are available on your website, you can translate a "
"product's information directly on the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/products/"
"product-form>`. Fields that support multiple languages are identifiable by "
"their abbreviation language (e.g., EN) next to their field."
msgstr ""
"Si plusieurs langues sont disponibles sur votre site web, vous pouvez "
"traduire les informations d'un produit directement sur le :ref:`formulaire "
"de produit <ecommerce/products/product-form>`. Les champs prenant en charge "
"plusieurs langues sont identifiables par leur abréviation de langue (par ex. "
"EN) à côté de leur champ."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:296
msgid "The eCommerce-related fields to translate are:"
msgstr "Les champs liés à l'eCommerce à traduire sont :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:298
msgid ":guilabel:`Product name`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Nom du produit`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:299
msgid ":guilabel:`Out-of-Stock Message` (under the :guilabel:`Sales` tab)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Message de rupture de stock` (sous l'onglet :guilabel:`Ventes`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:300
msgid ":guilabel:`Sales Description` (under the :guilabel:`Sales` tab)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:303
msgid ""
"Having untranslated content on a web page may be detrimental to the user "
"experience and :doc:`SEO <../../websites/website/structure/seo>`. You can "
"use the :doc:`Translate <../website/configuration/translate>` feature to "
"translate the page's content."
msgstr ""
"Avoir du contenu non traduit sur une page web peut nuire à l'expérience "
"utilisateur et au :doc:`SEO <../../websites/website/structure/seo>`. Vous "
"pouvez utiliser la fonctionnalité :doc:`Traduire <../website/configuration/"
"translate>` pour traduire le contenu de la page."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:306
msgid ""
"To check the language(s) of your website, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` and go to the :guilabel:`Website Info` section."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:312
msgid "Website availability"
msgstr "Disponibilité sur le site web"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:314
msgid ""
"To set the product's website availability, navigate to the :ref:`product "
"form <ecommerce/products/product-form>`, go to the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, "
"and in the :guilabel:`eCommerce shop` section, select "
"the :guilabel:`Website` you wish the product to be available on. Leave the "
"field blank to make the product available on *all* websites."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:320
msgid ""
"You can make a product available on either *one* website or *all* websites, "
"but selecting only *some* websites is not possible."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:326
msgid "Stock management"
msgstr "Gestion des stocks"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:328
msgid ""
"To enable and configure inventory management options, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section and the :guilabel:`Inventory "
"Defaults` sub-section."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:333
msgid ""
"The **Inventory** app must be installed to see the inventory management "
"options."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:334
msgid ""
"To display the stock level on the product page, the :guilabel:`Product Type` "
"field must be set to :guilabel:`Storable` in the :ref:`product form "
"<ecommerce/products/product-form>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:338
msgid "Inventory"
msgstr "Inventaire"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:340
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Inventory Defaults` sub-section, fill in those fields:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:342
msgid ""
":doc:`Warehouse <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/"
"inventory_management/warehouses>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:343
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Out-of-Stock`: Enable :guilabel:`Continue Selling` to allow "
"customers to place orders even when the product is **out of stock**. Leave "
"the box unchecked to **prevent orders**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:345
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Show Available Qty`: Displays the available quantity left under a "
"specified threshold on the product page. The available quantity is "
"calculated based on the :guilabel:`On hand` quantity minus the quantity "
"already reserved for outgoing transfers."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:352
msgid "Product comparison"
msgstr "Comparaison des produits"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:354
msgid ""
"To allow website visitors to compare products based on their attributes, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section, and enable :guilabel:`Product "
"Comparison Tool`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:358
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Compare`) icon is now available on each "
"product card on the main shop page when customers hover their mouse over it. "
"To compare products, customers can click the :icon:`fa-exchange` "
"(:guilabel:`Compare`) option on the products they want to compare, then "
"click :icon:`fa-exchange` :guilabel:`Compare` in the pop-up window at the "
"bottom of the page to reach the comparison summary."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:None
msgid "Product comparison window"
msgstr "Fenêtre de comparaison des produits"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:368
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Product Comparison Tool` is only available for products "
"with :ref:`attributes <ecommerce/products/product-variants>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:370
msgid ""
"Selecting the :icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Compare`) option from a "
"product page is also possible."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:376
msgid "Wishlists"
msgstr "Listes de souhaits"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:378
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-heart-o` :guilabel:`Add to wishlist` button allows customers "
"to add products to their wishlist, i.e., save them for later. To enable it, "
"go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down "
"to the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section, and "
"enable :guilabel:`Wishlists`. The button is available on each product page "
"and can be disabled in the :ref:`website editor <ecommerce/products/product-"
"page>` if needed."
msgstr ""
"Le bouton :icon:`fa-heart-o` :guilabel:`Ajouter à la liste de souhaits` "
"permet aux clients d'ajouter des produits à leur liste de souhaits, c'est-à-"
"dire de les enregistrer pour plus tard. Pour l'activer, allez dans "
":menuselection:`Site Web --> Configuration --> Paramètres`, faites défiler "
"jusqu'à la section :guilabel:`Boutique - Produits` et activez "
":guilabel:`Listes de souhaits`. Le bouton est disponible sur chaque page de "
"produit et peut être désactivé dans l':ref:`éditeur de Site Web <ecommerce/"
"products/product-page>` si nécessaire."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:None
msgid "Add to wishlist button"
msgstr "Bouton Ajouter à la liste de souhaits"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:388
msgid ""
"You can also display a :icon:`fa-heart-o` (:guilabel:`Wishlist`) button when "
"hovering the mouse over the product on the :ref:`shop page <ecommerce/"
"catalog/additional-features>`."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez également afficher un bouton :icon:`fa-heart-o` "
"(:guilabel:`Liste de souhaits`) lors du survol du produit avec la souris sur "
"la :ref:`page boutique <ecommerce/catalog/additional-features>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:390
msgid ""
"Customers can move products from their cart to their wishlist by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Save for later` button in the :guilabel:`Order "
"overview` :ref:`checkout step <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`."
msgstr ""
"Les clients peuvent déplacer des produits de leur panier vers leur liste de "
"souhaits en cliquant sur le bouton :guilabel:`Enregistrer pour plus tard` "
"dans l':guilabel:`étape de paiement` :ref:`Aperçu de la commande <ecommerce/"
"checkout/review_order>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:3
msgid "Catalog"
msgstr "Catalogue"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:5
msgid ""
"The eCommerce catalog displays products for customers to browse. It is "
"organized using product categories, available options, sorting, and "
"navigation paths. Essentially, the eCommerce catalog is the shop page of "
"your website."
msgstr ""
"Le catalogue eCommerce affiche les produits que les clients peuvent "
"parcourir. Il est organisé à l'aide de catégories de produits, d'options "
"disponibles, de tri et de chemins de navigation. Essentiellement, le "
"catalogue eCommerce est la page boutique de votre Site Web."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:9
msgid ""
"The product catalog includes a :ref:`top bar <ecommerce/catalog/top-bar>`, "
"a :ref:`side panel <ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>`, and a :ref:`product "
"listing area <ecommerce/catalog/product-listing>`. With Odoo, you "
"can :ref:`customize the layout <ecommerce/catalog/customize-layout>`, filter "
"by :ref:`categories and attributes <ecommerce/catalog/categories>`, and "
"use :ref:`additional features <ecommerce/catalog/additional-features>` "
"according to your needs."
msgstr ""
"Le catalogue de produits comprend une :ref:`barre supérieure <ecommerce/"
"catalog/top-bar>`, un :ref:`panneau latéral <ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>` "
"et une :ref:`zone de liste de produits <ecommerce/catalog/product-listing>`. "
"Avec Odoo, vous pouvez :ref:`personnaliser la mise en page <ecommerce/"
"catalog/customize-layout>`, filtrer par :ref:`catégories et attributs "
"<ecommerce/catalog/categories>` et utiliser des :ref:`fonctionnalités "
"supplémentaires <ecommerce/catalog/additional-features>` selon vos besoins."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:16
msgid ""
"You can customize the shop page using the website editor. To access it, go "
"to the shop page, click :guilabel:`Edit` in the upper-right corner, and "
"navigate to the :guilabel:`Customize` tab."
msgstr ""
"Personnaliser la page boutique à l'aide de l'éditeur de site web. Pour y "
"accéder, aller à la page boutique, cliquer sur :guilabel:`Modifier` dans le "
"coin supérieur droit et naviguer vers l'onglet :guilabel:`Personnaliser`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:22
msgid "Top bar"
msgstr "Barre supérieure"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:24
msgid ""
"The top bar can include a search bar, a currency selector, :ref:`sort-by and "
"display options <ecommerce/catalog/sort-by-and-display-option>`, "
"and :ref:`category quick access <ecommerce/catalog/categories>`."
msgstr ""
"La barre supérieure peut inclure une barre de recherche, un sélecteur de "
"devise, des :ref:`options de tri et d'affichage <ecommerce/catalog/sort-by-"
"and-display-option>` et un :ref:`accès rapide aux catégories <ecommerce/"
"catalog/categories>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:31
msgid "Sort-by search and display options"
msgstr "Options de recherche par tri et d'affichage"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:33
msgid ""
"You can toggle the :guilabel:`Search Bar`, display :ref:`categories "
"<ecommerce/catalog/categories>` and/or :ref:`attributes <ecommerce/catalog/"
"attributes>`, and enable or disable the :guilabel:`Sort-By` as well as "
"the :ref:`Layout <ecommerce/catalog/layout>` buttons in the :guilabel:`Top "
"Bar`."
msgstr ""
"Activer ou désactiver la :guilabel:`Barre de recherche`, afficher les "
":ref:`catégories <ecommerce/catalog/categories>` et/ou les :ref:`attributs "
"<ecommerce/catalog/attributes>` et activer ou désactiver les boutons "
":guilabel:`Trier par` ainsi que :ref:`Mise en page <ecommerce/catalog/layout>"
"` dans la :guilabel:`Barre supérieure`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:38
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Sort-by` button is toggled by default, and customers can "
"choose between the following :guilabel:`Default Sort` options:"
msgstr ""
"Le bouton :guilabel:`Trier par` est activé par défaut et les clients peuvent "
"choisir parmi les options :guilabel:`Tri par défaut` suivantes :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:41
msgid ":guilabel:`None`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Aucun`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:42
msgid ":guilabel:`Featured`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`En vedette`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:43
msgid ":guilabel:`Newest Arrivals`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Nouveautés`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:44
msgid ":guilabel:`Name (A-Z)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Nom (A-Z)`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:45
msgid ":guilabel:`Price - Low to High`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Prix - du plus bas au plus élevé`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:46
msgid ":guilabel:`Price - High to Low`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Prix - du plus élevé au plus bas`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:48
msgid ""
"The default sort applies to *all* :ref:`categories <ecommerce/catalog/"
"categories>`."
msgstr ""
"Le tri par défaut s'applique à *toutes* les :ref:`catégories <ecommerce/"
"catalog/categories>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:51
msgid ""
"If you don't want to display a top bar or :ref:`side panel <ecommerce/"
"catalog/side-panel>`, you can disable all related options in the website "
"editor."
msgstr ""
"Si vous ne souhaitez pas afficher de barre supérieure ou de :ref:`panneau "
"latéral <ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>`, désactiver toutes les options "
"associées dans l'éditeur de site web."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:57
msgid "Side panel"
msgstr "Panneau latéral"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:59
msgid ""
"The side panel provides advanced filtering tools to organize your product "
"categories. To further :ref:`categorize <ecommerce/catalog/categories>` the "
"shop page, you can activate various filters, such as the :ref:`attribute "
"<ecommerce/catalog/attributes>` filter."
msgstr ""
"Le panneau latéral fournit des outils de filtrage avancés pour organiser les "
"catégories de produits. Pour :ref:`catégoriser <ecommerce/catalog/categories>"
"` davantage la page boutique, activer différents filtres, tels que le filtre "
"par :ref:`attribut <ecommerce/catalog/attributes>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:63
msgid ""
"You can also add a :guilabel:`Datepicker` option to display a date range "
"calendar to check the availability of rental products over a specific "
"period. The :doc:`Rental app <../../../sales/rental>` must be installed to "
"use this feature."
msgstr ""
"Ajouter également une option :guilabel:`Sélecteur de date` pour afficher un "
"calendrier de plage de dates afin de vérifier la disponibilité des produits "
"de location sur une période spécifique. L'application :doc:`Location <../../"
"../sales/rental>` doit être installée pour utiliser cette fonctionnalité."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:67
msgid ""
"It is also possible to toggle the :guilabel:`Collapsible sidebar` switch to "
"make the side panel manually collapsible."
msgstr ""
"Il est également possible d'activer le commutateur :guilabel:`Barre latérale "
"rétractable` pour rendre le panneau latéral manuellement rétractable."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:71
msgid ""
"To use a price range or tags filter, you have to enable :ref:`attributes "
"<ecommerce/catalog/attributes>` first."
msgstr ""
"Pour utiliser un filtre de plage de prix ou d'étiquettes, activer d'abord "
"les :ref:`attributs <ecommerce/catalog/attributes>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:77
msgid "Product categorization in catalog"
msgstr "Catégorisation des produits dans le catalogue"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:79
msgid ""
"eCommerce categories are used to organize products into groups, making it "
"easier for customers to browse the online store."
msgstr ""
"Les catégories eCommerce permettent d'organiser les produits en groupes, "
"facilitant ainsi la navigation des clients dans la boutique en ligne."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:82
msgid ""
"To create eCommerce categories, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce "
"--> eCommerce Categories`, and click :guilabel:`New`. On the category form, "
"add a :guilabel:`Name`, optionally enter a :guilabel:`Parent Category`, and "
"write a :guilabel:`Category Description`, if needed."
msgstr ""
"Pour créer des catégories eCommerce, allez dans :menuselection:`Site Web --> "
"eCommerce --> Catégories eCommerce`, et cliquez sur :guilabel:`Nouveau`. Sur "
"le formulaire de catégorie, ajoutez un :guilabel:`Nom`, saisissez "
"éventuellement une :guilabel:`Catégorie parente`, et rédigez une "
":guilabel:`Description de catégorie`, si nécessaire."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:87
msgid ""
"To use eCommerce categories, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> "
"Products`, select the product you wish to modify, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, navigate to the :guilabel:`Ecommerce shop` "
"section, and select the :guilabel:`Categories` it belongs to."
msgstr ""
"Pour utiliser les catégories eCommerce, allez dans :menuselection:`Site "
"Web --> eCommerce --> Produits`, sélectionnez le produit que vous souhaitez "
"modifier, allez dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Ventes`, naviguez jusqu'à la "
"section :guilabel:`Boutique eCommerce`, et sélectionnez les "
":guilabel:`Catégories` auxquelles il appartient."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:92
msgid "A single product can belong to multiple eCommerce categories."
msgstr "Un seul produit peut appartenir à plusieurs catégories eCommerce."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:94
msgid ""
"Once the categories are configured and assigned to the relevant products, go "
"to the main shop page and open the website editor. In "
"the :guilabel:`Categories` option, you can either enable a menu on "
"the :guilabel:`Left`, i.e., in the :ref:`side panel <ecommerce/catalog/side-"
"panel>`, or on the :guilabel:`Top`, i.e., in the :ref:`top bar <ecommerce/"
"catalog/top-bar>`, or both. If you select the :guilabel:`Left` category, the "
"option :guilabel:`Collapsible Category Recursive` appears, allowing you to "
"collapse the category in the side panel."
msgstr ""
"Une fois les catégories configurées et assignées aux produits concernés, "
"allez sur la page principale de la boutique et ouvrez l'éditeur de site web. "
"Dans l'option :guilabel:`Catégories`, vous pouvez activer un menu à "
":guilabel:`Gauche`, c'est-à-dire dans le :ref:`panneau latéral <ecommerce/"
"catalog/side-panel>`, ou en :guilabel:`Haut`, c'est-à-dire dans la "
":ref:`barre supérieure <ecommerce/catalog/top-bar>`, ou les deux. Si vous "
"sélectionnez la catégorie :guilabel:`Gauche`, l'option :guilabel:`Catégorie "
"récursive repliable` apparaît, vous permettant de replier la catégorie dans "
"le panneau latéral."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:None
msgid "Categories options for your eCommerce website"
msgstr "Options des catégories de votre site web d'eCommerce"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:105
msgid ":doc:`../products`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:110
msgid "Attributes"
msgstr "Attributs"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:112
msgid ""
"Attributes refer to characteristics of a product, such as the color or "
"material, whereas variants are the different combinations of attributes. To "
"configure attributes and variants, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Products`, select a product, and click "
"the :guilabel:`Attributes & Variants` tab. Add as many attributes as desired."
msgstr ""
"Les attributs font référence aux caractéristiques d'un produit, telles que "
"la couleur ou le matériau, tandis que les variantes sont les différentes "
"combinaisons d'attributs. Pour configurer les attributs et les variantes, "
"allez dans :menuselection:`Site Web --> eCommerce --> Produits`, "
"sélectionnez un produit, et cliquez sur l'onglet :guilabel:`Attributs & "
"Variantes`. Ajoutez autant d'attributs que souhaité."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:118
msgid ":doc:`../../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:None
msgid "Attributes and variants of your product"
msgstr "Les attributs et les variantes de votre produit"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:123
msgid ""
"To enable attribute filtering, go to your main shop page, then open the "
"website editor, and set the :guilabel:`Attributes` field to :guilabel:`Left` "
"(:ref:`side panel <ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>`) and/or :guilabel:`Top` "
"(:ref:`top bar <ecommerce/catalog/top-bar>`)."
msgstr ""
"Pour activer le filtrage par attributs, allez sur la page principale de "
"votre boutique, puis ouvrez l'éditeur de site web, et définissez le champ "
":guilabel:`Attributs` sur :guilabel:`Gauche` (:ref:`panneau latéral "
"<ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>`) et/ou :guilabel:`Haut` (:ref:`barre "
"supérieure <ecommerce/catalog/top-bar>`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:129
msgid ""
"When attribute filtering is enabled in the top bar, customers must click "
"the :icon:`fa-sliders` (:guilabel:`dropdown toggle`) button to access it."
msgstr ""
"Lorsque le filtrage par attributs est activé dans la barre supérieure, les "
"clients doivent cliquer sur le bouton :icon:`fa-sliders` (:guilabel:`bascule "
"déroulante`) pour y accéder."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:132
msgid "When enabling :guilabel:`Attributes`, more options become available:"
msgstr ""
"Lors de l'activation des :guilabel:`Attributs`, d'autres options deviennent "
"disponibles :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:134
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Price Filter`: Toggle the switch to display a :guilabel:`Price "
"Range` bar, which allows customers to filter products according to a "
"specific price range by dragging adjustable handles."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Filtre de prix` : activer l'interrupteur pour afficher une barre "
":guilabel:`Fourchette de prix`, qui permet aux clients de filtrer les "
"produits selon une fourchette de prix spécifique en faisant glisser les "
"poignées ajustables."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:137
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Tags Filter`: Toggle the switch to display "
"the :guilabel:`Product Tags` on the shop page, and allow customers to filter "
"products using those tags by going to the :guilabel:`Tags` section in "
"the :ref:`side panel <ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Filtre par étiquettes produit` : Basculez l'interrupteur pour "
"afficher les :guilabel:`Étiquettes produit` sur la page de la boutique, et "
"permettre aux clients de filtrer les produits en utilisant ces étiquettes en "
"allant dans la section :guilabel:`Étiquettes` du :ref:`panneau latéral "
"<ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:142
msgid ""
"If you want to use tags on your e-commerce, go to :menuselection:`eCommerce "
"--> Product Tags` and click :guilabel:`New`. In the :guilabel:`Product "
"Templates` tab of the product tags form, add the products to link to the "
"given tag. You can also add product variants in the :guilabel:`Product "
"Variants` tab and view a summary of all selected products in "
"the :guilabel:`All Products` tab."
msgstr ""
"Si vous souhaitez utiliser des étiquettes sur votre eCommerce, allez dans "
":menuselection:`eCommerce --> Étiquettes produit` et cliquez sur "
":guilabel:`Nouveau`. Dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Modèles de produit` du "
"formulaire d'étiquettes produit, ajoutez les produits à lier à l'étiquette "
"donnée. Vous pouvez également ajouter des variantes de produits dans "
"l'onglet :guilabel:`Variantes de produit` et afficher un résumé de tous les "
"produits sélectionnés dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Tous les produits`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:147
msgid ""
"Price filtering works independently from attributes and, therefore, can be "
"enabled on its own, if desired."
msgstr ""
"Le filtrage par prix fonctionne indépendamment des attributs et peut donc "
"être activé seul, si désiré."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:153
msgid "Product listing area"
msgstr "Zone de liste de produits"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:155
msgid ""
"You can customize the layout of the entire shop page, as well as that "
"of :ref:`individual category pages <ecommerce/catalog/customize-layout>`."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez personnaliser la mise en page de l'ensemble de la page de "
"boutique, ainsi que celle des :ref:`pages de catégories individuelles "
"<ecommerce/catalog/customize-layout>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:159
msgid ""
"It is also possible to customize individual :ref:`product pages <ecommerce/"
"products/product-form>`."
msgstr ""
"Il est également possible de personnaliser les :ref:`pages produit "
"<ecommerce/products/product-form>` individuelles."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:163
msgid ""
"In the website editor, choose the :ref:`layout <ecommerce/catalog/sort-by-"
"and-display-option>`, and set the default layout to either :guilabel:`Grid` "
"or :guilabel:`List` view."
msgstr ""
"Dans l'éditeur de site web, choisissez la :ref:`mise en page <ecommerce/"
"catalog/sort-by-and-display-option>`, et définissez la mise en page par "
"défaut sur :guilabel:`Grille` ou vue :guilabel:`Liste`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:166
msgid "Use the following options to further adjust the layout:"
msgstr "Utilisez les options suivantes pour ajuster davantage la mise en page :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:168
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Size`: Set the number of products displayed per page and line."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Taille` : définir le nombre de produits affichés par page et par "
"ligne."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:169
msgid ":guilabel:`Gap`: Define the gap between the products."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Espacement` : Définissez l'espace entre les produits."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:170
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Style`: "
"Select :guilabel:`Default`, :guilabel:`Cards`, :guilabel:`Thumbnails`, "
"or :guilabel:`Grid`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Style` : sélectionner :guilabel:`Par défaut`, :guilabel:`Cartes`, "
":guilabel:`Vignettes` ou :guilabel:`Grille`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:172
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Image Size`: Choose the aspect ratio for the product "
"images: :guilabel:`Landscape (4/3)`, :guilabel:`Default "
"(1/1)`, :guilabel:`Portrait (4/5)`, or :guilabel:`Vertical (2/3)`. You can "
"also adjust the display by changing the :guilabel:`Fill` options to fit your "
"design preferences best."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Taille d'image` : Choisissez le rapport hauteur/largeur pour les "
"images de produit : :guilabel:`Paysage (4/3)`, :guilabel:`Par défaut (1/1)`, "
":guilabel:`Portrait (4/5)`, ou :guilabel:`Vertical (2/3)`. Vous pouvez "
"également ajuster l'affichage en modifiant les options de "
":guilabel:`Remplissage` pour correspondre au mieux à vos préférences de "
"conception."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:177
msgid ""
"Toggle the :guilabel:`Prod. Desc.` switch to display the product description "
"below the product's name."
msgstr ""
"Basculez l'interrupteur :guilabel:`Descr. prod.` pour afficher la "
"description du produit sous le nom du produit."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:181
msgid ""
"You can choose the size of the grid, but be aware that displaying too many "
"products may affect performance and page loading speed."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez choisir la taille de la grille, mais sachez que l'affichage d'un "
"trop grand nombre de produits peut nuire aux performances et à la vitesse de "
"chargement des pages."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:184
msgid ""
"In addition, you can manually change a product’s position on the shop page. "
"To do so, go to the main shop page, click the product, and open the website "
"editor. In the :guilabel:`Product` section, you can reorder the products by "
"using the arrows. The `<<` `>>` buttons allow to move the product to the "
"extreme left or right, and `<` `>` allow to move it one row to the left or "
"right."
msgstr ""
"De plus, vous pouvez modifier manuellement la position d'un produit sur la "
"page de la boutique. Pour ce faire, allez sur la page principale de la "
"boutique, cliquez sur le produit, et ouvrez l'éditeur de site web. Dans la "
"section :guilabel:`Produit`, vous pouvez réorganiser les produits en "
"utilisant les flèches. Les boutons `<<` `>>` permettent de déplacer le "
"produit à l'extrême gauche ou droite, et `<` `>` permettent de le déplacer "
"d'une ligne à gauche ou à droite."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:190
msgid ""
"It is also possible to change the products' positions on the shop page by "
"going to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products`, switching to "
"the list view, and dragging and dropping the products within the list."
msgstr ""
"Il est également possible de modifier les positions des produits sur la page "
"boutique en allant à :menuselection:`Site Web --> eCommerce --> Produits`, "
"en passant à la vue liste, et en glissant-déposant les produits dans la "
"liste."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:195
msgid "Product highlight"
msgstr "Mise en évidence des produits"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:197
msgid ""
"You can highlight products to make them more visible on the shop page. To do "
"so, go to the website editor and click the product to highlight. In "
"the :guilabel:`Product` section, you can choose the size of the product "
"image by clicking the grid, and you can also add a :guilabel:`Ribbon`. This "
"displays a banner across the product's image, such "
"as :guilabel:`Sale`, :guilabel:`Sold out`, :guilabel:`Out of stock` "
"or :guilabel:`New!`."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez mettre en évidence des produits pour les rendre plus visibles "
"sur la page de la boutique. Pour ce faire, allez dans l'éditeur de site web "
"et cliquez sur le produit à mettre en évidence. Dans la section "
":guilabel:`Produit`, vous pouvez choisir la taille de l'image du produit en "
"cliquant sur la grille, et vous pouvez également ajouter un "
":guilabel:`Ruban`. Cela affiche une bannière sur l'image du produit, telle "
"que :guilabel:`Promotion`, :guilabel:`Épuisé`, :guilabel:`En rupture de "
"stock` ou :guilabel:`Nouveau !`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:None
msgid "Ribbon highlight"
msgstr "Mise en évidence par ruban"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:206
msgid ""
"To create a new ribbon, click the green :icon:`fa-plus` (:guilabel:`Create`) "
"icon next to the :guilabel:`Ribbon` field. Then add a :guilabel:`Ribbon "
"name`, define its :guilabel:`Position`, and choose a :guilabel:`Background` "
"and a :guilabel:`Text` label. To edit the ribbon, click the :icon:`fa-pencil-"
"square-o` (:guilabel:`Edit`) icon next to the :guilabel:`Ribbon` label."
msgstr ""
"Pour créer un nouveau ruban, cliquez sur l'icône verte :icon:`fa-plus` "
"(:guilabel:`Créer`) à côté du champ :guilabel:`Ruban`. Ajoutez ensuite un "
":guilabel:`Nom du ruban`, définissez sa :guilabel:`Position`, et choisissez "
"un :guilabel:`Arrière-plan` et une étiquette :guilabel:`Texte`. Pour "
"modifier le ruban, cliquez sur l'icône :icon:`fa-pencil-square-o` "
"(:guilabel:`Modifier`) à côté de l'étiquette :guilabel:`Ruban`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:None
msgid "Create a new ribbon."
msgstr "Créer un nouveau ruban."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:214
msgid "The ribbon is now available for all the eCommerce products."
msgstr "Le ruban est maintenant disponible pour tous les produits eCommerce."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:217
msgid "There are other ways to create a new ribbon:"
msgstr "Il existe d'autres façons de créer un nouveau ruban :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:219
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Product Ribbons` and "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Aller à :menuselection:`Site Web --> eCommerce --> Rubans de produit` et "
"cliquer sur :guilabel:`Nouveau`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:220
msgid ""
"Activate the :doc:`developer mode <../../../general/developer_mode>`, access "
"the product form, and under the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, change or create the "
"ribbon in the :guilabel:`Ribbon` field."
msgstr ""
"Activer le :doc:`mode développeur <../../../general/developer_mode>`, "
"accéder au formulaire du produit, et sous l'onglet :guilabel:`Ventes`, "
"modifier ou créer le ruban dans le champ :guilabel:`Ruban`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:224
msgid ""
"It is also possible to add ribbons for specific :ref:`product variants "
"<ecommerce/products/product-variants>`. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products` and select a product. "
"Click the :guilabel:`Variants` smart button, choose a variant, and add a "
"ribbon in the :guilabel:`Variant Ribbon` field of the :guilabel:`Sales` "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Il est également possible d'ajouter des rubans pour des :ref:`variantes de "
"produit <ecommerce/products/product-variants>` spécifiques. Pour ce faire, "
"aller à :menuselection:`Site Web --> eCommerce --> Produits` et sélectionner "
"un produit. Cliquer sur le bouton intelligent :guilabel:`Variantes`, choisir "
"une variante, et ajouter un ruban dans le champ :guilabel:`Ruban de "
"variante` de la section :guilabel:`Ventes`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:233
msgid "Shop and category page design"
msgstr "Conception de la page boutique et catégorie"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:235
msgid ""
"Use :doc:`building blocks <../../website/web_design/building_blocks>` to add "
"content on the shop and/or category page."
msgstr ""
"Utiliser les :doc:`blocs de construction <../../website/web_design/"
"building_blocks>` pour ajouter du contenu sur la page boutique et/ou "
"catégorie."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:238
msgid ""
"You can customize the top and/or bottom section of the catalog, either for "
"the entire shop page or for a specific category. In the latter case, the "
"block appears *only* when filtering by that category. To do so, move the "
"block to the far top or bottom section to display it on the general shop "
"page or to the area below the category's name at the top or beneath the "
"product list to display it only when filtering by that specific category."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez personnaliser la section supérieure et/ou inférieure du "
"catalogue, soit pour l'ensemble de la page boutique, soit pour une catégorie "
"spécifique. Dans ce dernier cas, le bloc apparaît *uniquement* lors du "
"filtrage par cette catégorie. Pour ce faire, déplacez le bloc vers la "
"section tout en haut ou tout en bas pour l'afficher sur la page boutique "
"générale ou vers la zone en dessous du nom de la catégorie en haut ou sous "
"la liste des produits pour l'afficher uniquement lors du filtrage par cette "
"catégorie spécifique."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:0
msgid "Place building block in the header or footer."
msgstr "Placer le bloc de construction dans l'en-tête ou le pied de page."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:248
msgid ""
"Adding content to an eCommerce category page helps improve the :doc:`SEO "
"<../../website/structure/seo>` strategy. Using keywords linked to the "
"products or the eCommerce categories can also increase organic traffic. "
"Additionally, each category has its own specific URL that can be pointed to "
"and is indexed by search engines."
msgstr ""
"Ajouter du contenu à une page de catégorie eCommerce aide à améliorer la "
"stratégie :doc:`SEO <../../website/structure/seo>`. Utiliser des mots-clés "
"liés aux produits ou aux catégories eCommerce peut également augmenter le "
"trafic organique. De plus, chaque catégorie possède sa propre URL spécifique "
"qui peut être pointée et qui est indexée par les moteurs de recherche."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:252
msgid ""
"eCommerce categories can also be added as :ref:`mega menu items <website/"
"header_footer/mega-menus>` for quick access."
msgstr ""
"Les catégories eCommerce peuvent également être ajoutées comme "
":ref:`éléments de méga menu <website/header_footer/mega-menus>` pour un "
"accès rapide."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:260
msgid ""
"You can access and enable additional feature buttons such as "
"a :guilabel:`Add to cart` or :guilabel:`Wishlist` button or "
"a :guilabel:`Comparison list`. To do so, open the website editor, click the "
"desired feature buttons. All three buttons appear when hovering the mouse "
"over a product's image."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez accéder et activer des boutons de fonctionnalités "
"supplémentaires tels qu'un bouton :guilabel:`Ajouter au panier` ou "
":guilabel:`Liste de souhaits` ou une :guilabel:`Liste de comparaison`. Pour "
"ce faire, ouvrir l'éditeur de site web, cliquer sur les boutons de "
"fonctionnalités souhaités. Les trois boutons apparaissent au survol de "
"l'image d'un produit."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:265
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-shopping-cart` (:guilabel:`Add to cart`): adds a button "
"to :doc:`add the product to the cart <../checkout>`;"
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-shopping-cart` (:guilabel:`Ajouter au panier`) : ajoute un bouton "
"pour :doc:`ajouter le produit au panier <../checkout>` ;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:267
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Compare`): adds a button to compare products "
"based on their price, variant, etc.;"
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Comparer`) : ajoute un bouton pour comparer "
"les produits en fonction de leur prix, variante, etc. ;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:269
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-heart-o` (:guilabel:`Wishlist`): adds a button to :ref:`wishlist "
"<ecommerce/products/wishlists>` the product."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-heart-o` (:guilabel:`Liste de souhaits`) : ajoute un bouton pour "
":ref:`ajouter le produit à la liste de souhaits <ecommerce/products/"
"wishlists>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:274
msgid ":doc:`Products <../products>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Produits <../products>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:3
msgid "Cross-selling and upselling"
msgstr "Ventes croisée et incitative"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:5
msgid ""
":ref:`Cross-selling <ecommerce/cross_selling>` and :ref:`upselling "
"<ecommerce/cross_upselling/alternative>` are sales techniques designed to "
"encourage customers to purchase additional or higher-priced products and "
"services from your :doc:`catalog`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:12
msgid "Cross-selling"
msgstr "Vente croisée"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:14
msgid ""
"Cross-selling can be achieved by suggesting :ref:`optional products "
"<ecommerce/cross_upselling/optional>` when items are added to the cart or by "
"recommending :ref:`accessory products <ecommerce/cross_upselling/accessory>` "
"on the checkout page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:21
msgid "Optional products"
msgstr "Produits optionnels"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Optional products** are suggested when the customer selects a product and "
"clicks :guilabel:`Add to cart`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:26
msgid ""
"To enable **optional products**, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce "
"--> Products`, select a product, go to the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, and enter "
"the products you wish to feature in the :guilabel:`Optional Products` field."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:None
msgid "Optional products cross-selling"
msgstr "Produits optionnels en vente croisée"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:36
msgid "Accessory products"
msgstr "Produits accessoires"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:38
msgid ""
"**Accessory products** are showcased in the :guilabel:`Suggested "
"Accessories` section during the :guilabel:`Review Order` step, just before "
"proceeding to checkout."
msgstr ""
"Les **produits accessoires** sont présentés dans la section "
":guilabel:`Accessoires suggérés` lors de l'étape :guilabel:`Vérifier la "
"commande`, juste avant de procéder au paiement."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:41
msgid ""
"To enable **accessory products**, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Products`, select a product, go to the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, "
"and enter the products you wish to feature in the :guilabel:`Accessory "
"Products` field."
msgstr ""
"Pour activer les **produits accessoires**, allez dans :menuselection:`Site "
"Web --> eCommerce --> Produits`, sélectionnez un produit, allez dans "
"l'onglet :guilabel:`Ventes`, et saisissez les produits que vous souhaitez "
"présenter dans le champ :guilabel:`Produits accessoires`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:None
msgid "Suggested accessories at checkout during cart review"
msgstr ""
"Les accessoires suggérés lors du paiement pendant la vérification du panier."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:51
msgid "Upselling"
msgstr "Vente incitative"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:53
msgid ""
"You can display **alternative products** at the bottom of the product page "
"as an upselling technique, encouraging customers to consider a more "
"expensive variant or product than their initial choice by presenting "
"appealing alternatives."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez afficher des **produits alternatifs** en bas de la page produit "
"comme technique de montée en gamme, en encourageant les clients à considérer "
"une variante ou un produit plus cher que leur choix initial en présentant "
"des alternatives attrayantes."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:None
msgid "Alternative products on the product page"
msgstr "Les produits alternatifs sur la page du produit"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:60
msgid ""
"To enable alternative products, navigate to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Products`, select the desired product, and go to "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` tab. In the :guilabel:`Alternative Products` field, "
"add the products you want to feature."
msgstr ""
"Pour activer les produits alternatifs, accédez à :menuselection:`Site "
"Web --> eCommerce --> Produits`, sélectionnez le produit souhaité, et allez "
"dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Ventes`. Dans le champ :guilabel:`Produits "
"alternatifs`, ajoutez les produits que vous souhaitez présenter."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:64
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Go to Website` to view the alternative products displayed "
"at the bottom of the product page."
msgstr ""
"Cliquer sur :guilabel:`Aller sur le site Web` pour voir les produits "
"alternatifs affichés en bas de la page produit."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:67
msgid ""
"To adjust the settings, click :guilabel:`Edit` and select the "
"related :doc:`building block <../../website/web_design/building_blocks>`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, scroll to the :guilabel:`Alternative "
"Products` section and modify the settings as needed to tailor the display to "
"your preferences."
msgstr ""
"Pour ajuster les paramètres, cliquer sur :guilabel:`Modifier` et "
"sélectionner le :doc:`bloc de construction <../../website/web_design/"
"building_blocks>` associé. Dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Personnaliser`, faire "
"défiler jusqu'à la section :guilabel:`Produits alternatifs` et modifier les "
"paramètres selon les besoins pour adapter l'affichage à vos préférences."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo offers multiple options to configure prices on the ecommerce. For "
"example, you can apply :ref:`prices per unit <ecommerce/prices/price-per-"
"unit>`, offer :ref:`discounts <ecommerce/prices/discounts>`, and set "
"up :ref:`pricelists <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:12
msgid "Taxes"
msgstr "Taxes"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:14
msgid ""
"To add a tax on a product, you can either set a tax in "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Taxes` field of the **product template** or "
"use :doc:`fiscal positions </applications/finance/accounting/taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>`."
msgstr ""
"Pour ajouter une taxe sur un produit, vous pouvez soit définir une taxe dans "
"le champ :guilabel:`Taxes clients` du **modèle de produit**, soit utiliser "
"des :doc:`positions fiscales </applications/finance/accounting/taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:19
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/taxes`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/taxes`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:20
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:24
msgid ""
"Choosing the displayed price tax usually depends on a country's regulations "
"or the type of customers (:doc:`B2B vs. B2C <../b2b_b2c>`). To select the "
"type of price displayed, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, select the website, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Shop - "
"Products` section, and under :guilabel:`Display Product Prices` select "
"between:"
msgstr ""
"Le choix de la taxe du prix affiché dépend généralement des réglementations "
"d'un pays ou du type de clients (:doc:`B2B vs. B2C <../b2b_b2c>`). Pour "
"sélectionner le type de prix affiché, allez dans :menuselection:`Site "
"Web --> Configuration --> Paramètres`, sélectionnez le site Web, faites "
"défiler jusqu'à la section :guilabel:`Boutique - Produits`, et sous "
":guilabel:`Afficher les prix des produits`, choisissez entre :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:29
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tax Excluded`: the price displayed on the website is tax-"
"excluded, and the tax is computed at the :ref:`order review <ecommerce/"
"checkout/review_order>` step;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:31
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tax Included`: the price displayed on the website is tax-included."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Taxes incluses` : le prix affiché sur le site est toutes taxes "
"comprises."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:34
msgid ""
"This setting is website-specific and can therefore be configured "
"independently for every website in the database."
msgstr ""
"Ce paramètre est spécifique au site et peut donc être configuré "
"indépendamment pour chaque site dans la base de données."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:38
msgid ""
"Switch the :ref:`Tax indication <ecommerce/products/product-presentation>` "
"toggle on in the website editor to explicitly indicate if the price is `Tax "
"excluded` or `Tax included` on the product page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:41
msgid ""
"Enable specific :ref:`B2B fields <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/b2b-fields>` in "
"the :ref:`delivery step <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>` during the checkout "
"using the :doc:`website editor </applications/websites/website/web_design>`."
msgstr ""
"Activer des :ref:`champs B2B <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/b2b-fields>` spécifiques "
"dans l':ref:`étape de livraison <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>` lors du "
"paiement à l'aide de l':doc:`éditeur de site web </applications/websites/"
"website/web_design>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:48
msgid "Price per unit"
msgstr "Prix à l'unité"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:50
msgid ""
"To display a :doc:`price per unit </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"product_management/configure/uom>` alongside the sales price on the product "
"page, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Pour afficher un :doc:`prix unitaire </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/product_management/configure/uom>` à côté du prix de vente sur la "
"page du produit, procéder comme suit :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:54
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll to "
"the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section, and enable :guilabel:`Product "
"Reference Price`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:56
msgid ""
":ref:`Navigate to the product form <ecommerce/products/create-products>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:57
msgid ""
"Set the product's :guilabel:`Sales price` and select the unit "
"(e.g., :guilabel:`Units`)."
msgstr ""
"Définir le :guilabel:`Prix de vente` du produit et sélectionner l'unité (par "
"ex., :guilabel:`Unités`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:58
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Base Unit Count` field, enter the number of units in the "
"product, then select the relevant unit from the dropdown list."
msgstr ""
"Dans le champ :guilabel:`nombre d'unités de base`, saisir le nombre d'unités "
"dans le produit, puis sélectionner l'unité concernée dans la liste "
"déroulante."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:62
msgid ""
"Imagine you want to sell a 2-liter bucket of paint for $60, i.e., $30 per "
"liter."
msgstr ""
"Imaginons que vous souhaitiez vendre un seau de peinture de 2 litres pour 60 "
"$, soit 30 $ par litre."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:0
msgid "Cost per unit pricing on the product form."
msgstr "Prix unitaire sur le formulaire produit."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:67
msgid ""
"The price per units, in this case per liter, is shown next to the sales "
"price on the product page."
msgstr ""
"Le prix unitaire, dans ce cas par litre, s'affiche à côté du prix de vente "
"sur la page du produit."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:0
msgid "Unit pricing on the product page."
msgstr "Prix unitaire sur la page du produit."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:74
msgid "The price per unit may be mandatory in some countries."
msgstr "Le prix unitaire peut être obligatoire dans certains pays."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:77
msgid ""
":doc:`/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/"
"uom`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/"
