"Go back to Google Workspace, tick the box at the bottom, and "
"click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Retournez sur Google Workspace, cochez la case au bas de la page, puis "
"cliquez sur :guilabel:`Confirmer`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:181
msgid ""
"`Google Workspace Admin Help: Verify your domain with a TXT record <https://"
"support.google.com/a/answer/16018515>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Aide de l’administrateur Google Workspace : vérifier votre domaine avec un "
"enregistrement TXT <https://support.google.com/a/answer/16018515>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:185
msgid "Redirect emails to Gmail"
msgstr "Rediriger les e-mails vers Gmail"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:187
msgid ""
"Open the `database manager <https://www.odoo.com/my/databases>`_, click "
"the :icon:`fa-gear` (:guilabel:`gear`) button next to the database name and "
"select :icon:`fa-globe` :guilabel:`Domain Names`. Click :guilabel:`DNS`, "
"then :guilabel:`Add DNS record`, and select :guilabel:`MX`."
msgstr ""
"Ouvrez le `gestionnaire de bases de données <https://www.odoo.com/my/"
"databases>`_, cliquez sur le bouton :icon:`fa-gear` (:guilabel:`engrenage`) "
"à côté du nom de la base de données et sélectionnez :icon:`fa-"
"globe` :guilabel:`Noms de domaine`. Cliquez sur :guilabel:`DNS`, "
"puis :guilabel:`Ajouter un enregistrement DNS`, et "
"sélectionnez :guilabel:`MX`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:191
msgid ""
"Enter `@` in the :guilabel:`Name` field, `1` in the :guilabel:`Priority` "
"field, `smtp.google.com.` in the :guilabel:`Content` field, and "
